325static ::mlir::LogicalResult __mlir_ods_local_region_constraint_Ops0(
326 ::mlir::Operation *op, ::mlir::Region &region, ::llvm::StringRef regionName,
327 unsigned regionIndex) {
328 if (!((::llvm::hasNItems(region, 1)))) {
329 return op->emitOpError("region #") << regionIndex
330 << (regionName.empty() ? " " : " ('" + regionName + "') ")
331 << "failed to verify constraint: region with 1 blocks";
332 }
333 return ::mlir::success();
334}
335
336static ::mlir::LogicalResult __mlir_ods_local_region_constraint_Ops1(
337 ::mlir::Operation *op, ::mlir::Region &region, ::llvm::StringRef regionName,
338 unsigned regionIndex) {
339 if (!((::llvm::hasNItemsOrLess(region, 1)))) {
340 return op->emitOpError("region #") << regionIndex
341 << (regionName.empty() ? " " : " ('" + regionName + "') ")
342 << "failed to verify constraint: region with at most 1 blocks";
343 }
344 return ::mlir::success();
345}

417void AddOp::build(::mlir::OpBuilder &odsBuilder, ::mlir::OperationState &odsState, ::mlir::Type out, ::mlir::Value lhs, ::mlir::Value rhs) {
418 odsState.addOperands(lhs);
419 odsState.addOperands(rhs);
420 odsState.addTypes(out);
421}

423void AddOp::build(::mlir::OpBuilder &odsBuilder, ::mlir::OperationState &odsState, ::mlir::TypeRange resultTypes, ::mlir::Value lhs, ::mlir::Value rhs) {
424 odsState.addOperands(lhs);
425 odsState.addOperands(rhs);
426 assert(resultTypes.size() == 1u && "mismatched number of results");
427 odsState.addTypes(resultTypes);
428}
429
430void AddOp::build(::mlir::OpBuilder &, ::mlir::OperationState &odsState, ::mlir::TypeRange resultTypes, ::mlir::ValueRange operands, ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::NamedAttribute> attributes) {
431 assert(operands.size() == 2u && "mismatched number of parameters");
432 odsState.addOperands(operands);
433 odsState.addAttributes(attributes);
434 assert(resultTypes.size() == 1u && "mismatched number of return types");
435 odsState.addTypes(resultTypes);
436}
437
438::mlir::LogicalResult AddOp::verifyInvariantsImpl() {
439 {
440 unsigned index = 0; (void)index;
441 auto valueGroup0 = getODSOperands(0);
442
443 for (auto v : valueGroup0) {
444 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_type_constraint_Ops0(*this, v.getType(), "operand", index++)))
445 return ::mlir::failure();
446 }
447 auto valueGroup1 = getODSOperands(1);
448
449 for (auto v : valueGroup1) {
450 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_type_constraint_Ops0(*this, v.getType(), "operand", index++)))
451 return ::mlir::failure();
452 }
453 }
454 {
455 unsigned index = 0; (void)index;
456 auto valueGroup0 = getODSResults(0);
457
458 for (auto v : valueGroup0) {
459 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_type_constraint_Ops0(*this, v.getType(), "result", index++)))
460 return ::mlir::failure();
461 }
462 }
463 return ::mlir::success();
464}
465
466::mlir::LogicalResult AddOp::verifyInvariants() {
467 return verifyInvariantsImpl();
468}
469
470::mlir::ParseResult AddOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
471 ::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand lhsRawOperands[1];
472 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand> lhsOperands(lhsRawOperands); ::llvm::SMLoc lhsOperandsLoc;
473 (void)lhsOperandsLoc;
474 ::mlir::Type lhsRawTypes[1];
475 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> lhsTypes(lhsRawTypes);
476 ::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand rhsRawOperands[1];
477 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand> rhsOperands(rhsRawOperands); ::llvm::SMLoc rhsOperandsLoc;
478 (void)rhsOperandsLoc;
479 ::mlir::Type rhsRawTypes[1];
480 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> rhsTypes(rhsRawTypes);
481 ::mlir::Type outRawTypes[1];
482 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> outTypes(outRawTypes);
483
484 lhsOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
485 if (parser.parseOperand(lhsRawOperands[0]))
486 return ::mlir::failure();
487 if (parser.parseColon())
488 return ::mlir::failure();
489
490 {
491 ::zml::ComponentType type;
492 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
493 return ::mlir::failure();
494 lhsRawTypes[0] = type;
495 }
496 if (parser.parseComma())
497 return ::mlir::failure();
498
499 rhsOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
500 if (parser.parseOperand(rhsRawOperands[0]))
501 return ::mlir::failure();
502 if (parser.parseColon())
503 return ::mlir::failure();
504
505 {
506 ::zml::ComponentType type;
507 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
508 return ::mlir::failure();
509 rhsRawTypes[0] = type;
510 }
511 if (parser.parseArrow())
512 return ::mlir::failure();
513
514 {
515 ::zml::ComponentType type;
516 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
517 return ::mlir::failure();
518 outRawTypes[0] = type;
519 }
520 {
521 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
522 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
523 return ::mlir::failure();
524 }
525 result.addTypes(outTypes);
526 if (parser.resolveOperands(lhsOperands, lhsTypes, lhsOperandsLoc, result.operands))
527 return ::mlir::failure();
528 if (parser.resolveOperands(rhsOperands, rhsTypes, rhsOperandsLoc, result.operands))
529 return ::mlir::failure();
530 return ::mlir::success();
531}
532
533void AddOp::print(::mlir::OpAsmPrinter &_odsPrinter) {
534 _odsPrinter << ' ';
535 _odsPrinter << getLhs();
536 _odsPrinter << ' ' << ":";
537 _odsPrinter << ' ';
538 {
539 auto type = getLhs().getType();
540 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::zml::ComponentType>(type))
541 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
542 else
543 _odsPrinter << type;
544 }
545 _odsPrinter << ",";
546 _odsPrinter << ' ';
547 _odsPrinter << getRhs();
548 _odsPrinter << ' ' << ":";
549 _odsPrinter << ' ';
550 {
551 auto type = getRhs().getType();
552 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::zml::ComponentType>(type))
553 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
554 else
555 _odsPrinter << type;
556 }
557 _odsPrinter << ' ' << "->";
558 _odsPrinter << ' ';
559 {
560 auto type = getOut().getType();
561 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::zml::ComponentType>(type))
562 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
563 else
564 _odsPrinter << type;
565 }
566 ::llvm::SmallVector<::llvm::StringRef, 2> elidedAttrs;
567 _odsPrinter.printOptionalAttrDict((*this)->getAttrs(), elidedAttrs);
568}

570void AddOp::getEffects(::llvm::SmallVectorImpl<::mlir::SideEffects::EffectInstance<::mlir::MemoryEffects::Effect>> &effects) {
571}

962
963::mlir::ParseResult BitAndOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
964 ::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand lhsRawOperands[1];
965 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand> lhsOperands(lhsRawOperands); ::llvm::SMLoc lhsOperandsLoc;
966 (void)lhsOperandsLoc;
967 ::mlir::Type lhsRawTypes[1];
968 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> lhsTypes(lhsRawTypes);
969 ::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand rhsRawOperands[1];
970 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand> rhsOperands(rhsRawOperands); ::llvm::SMLoc rhsOperandsLoc;
971 (void)rhsOperandsLoc;
972 ::mlir::Type rhsRawTypes[1];
973 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> rhsTypes(rhsRawTypes);
974 ::mlir::Type outRawTypes[1];
975 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> outTypes(outRawTypes);
976
977 lhsOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
978 if (parser.parseOperand(lhsRawOperands[0]))
979 return ::mlir::failure();
980 if (parser.parseColon())
981 return ::mlir::failure();
982
983 {
984 ::zml::ComponentType type;
985 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
986 return ::mlir::failure();
987 lhsRawTypes[0] = type;
988 }
989 if (parser.parseComma())
990 return ::mlir::failure();
991
992 rhsOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
993 if (parser.parseOperand(rhsRawOperands[0]))
994 return ::mlir::failure();
995 if (parser.parseColon())
996 return ::mlir::failure();
997
998 {
999 ::zml::ComponentType type;
1000 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
1001 return ::mlir::failure();
1002 rhsRawTypes[0] = type;
1003 }
1004 if (parser.parseArrow())
1005 return ::mlir::failure();
1006
1007 {
1008 ::zml::ComponentType type;
1009 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
1010 return ::mlir::failure();
1011 outRawTypes[0] = type;
1012 }
1013 {
1014 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
1015 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
1016 return ::mlir::failure();
1017 }
1018 result.addTypes(outTypes);
1019 if (parser.resolveOperands(lhsOperands, lhsTypes, lhsOperandsLoc, result.operands))
1020 return ::mlir::failure();
1021 if (parser.resolveOperands(rhsOperands, rhsTypes, rhsOperandsLoc, result.operands))
1022 return ::mlir::failure();
1023 return ::mlir::success();
1024}

1033 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::zml::ComponentType>(type))
1034 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
1035 else
1036 _odsPrinter << type;
1037 }
1038 _odsPrinter << ",";
1039 _odsPrinter << ' ';
1040 _odsPrinter << getRhs();
1041 _odsPrinter << ' ' << ":";
1042 _odsPrinter << ' ';
1043 {
1044 auto type = getRhs().getType();
1045 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::zml::ComponentType>(type))
1046 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
1047 else
1048 _odsPrinter << type;
1049 }
1050 _odsPrinter << ' ' << "->";
1051 _odsPrinter << ' ';
1052 {

1055 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
1056 else
1057 _odsPrinter << type;
1058 }

1177::mlir::LogicalResult ComponentOpAdaptor::verify(::mlir::Location loc) {
1178 auto tblgen_builtin = getProperties().builtin; (void)tblgen_builtin;
1179 auto tblgen_function = getProperties().function; (void)tblgen_function;
1180 auto tblgen_generic = getProperties().generic; (void)tblgen_generic;
1181 auto tblgen_params = getProperties().params; (void)tblgen_params;
1182 auto tblgen_sym_name = getProperties().sym_name; (void)tblgen_sym_name;
1183 if (!tblgen_sym_name) return emitError(loc, "'zml.component' op ""requires attribute 'sym_name'");
1184 auto tblgen_usesBackVariables = getProperties().usesBackVariables; (void)tblgen_usesBackVariables;
1185
1186 if (tblgen_sym_name && !((::llvm::isa<::mlir::StringAttr>(tblgen_sym_name))))
1187 return emitError(loc, "'zml.component' op ""attribute 'sym_name' failed to satisfy constraint: string attribute");
1188
1189 if (tblgen_function && !((::llvm::isa<::mlir::UnitAttr>(tblgen_function))))
1190 return emitError(loc, "'zml.component' op ""attribute 'function' failed to satisfy constraint: unit attribute");
1191
1192 if (tblgen_generic && !((::llvm::isa<::mlir::UnitAttr>(tblgen_generic))))
1193 return emitError(loc, "'zml.component' op ""attribute 'generic' failed to satisfy constraint: unit attribute");
1194
1195 if (tblgen_builtin && !((::llvm::isa<::mlir::UnitAttr>(tblgen_builtin))))
1196 return emitError(loc, "'zml.component' op ""attribute 'builtin' failed to satisfy constraint: unit attribute");
1197
1198 if (tblgen_usesBackVariables && !((::llvm::isa<::mlir::UnitAttr>(tblgen_usesBackVariables))))
1199 return emitError(loc, "'zml.component' op ""attribute 'usesBackVariables' failed to satisfy constraint: unit attribute");
1200
1201 if (tblgen_params && !(((::llvm::isa<::mlir::ArrayAttr>(tblgen_params))) && (::llvm::all_of(::llvm::cast<::mlir::ArrayAttr>(tblgen_params), [&](::mlir::Attribute attr) { return attr && ((::llvm::isa<::mlir::FlatSymbolRefAttr>(attr))); }))))
1202 return emitError(loc, "'zml.component' op ""attribute 'params' failed to satisfy constraint: flat symbol ref array attribute");
1203 return ::mlir::success();
1204}

1207 return {index, 1};

1213 std::next(getOperation()->operand_begin(), valueRange.first + valueRange.second)};

1230::mlir::LogicalResult ComponentOp::setPropertiesFromAttr(Properties &prop, ::mlir::Attribute attr, ::llvm::function_ref<::mlir::InFlightDiagnostic()> emitError) {
1231 ::mlir::DictionaryAttr dict = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::mlir::DictionaryAttr>(attr);
1232 if (!dict) {
1233 emitError() << "expected DictionaryAttr to set properties";
1234 return ::mlir::failure();
1235 }
1236
1237 {
1238 auto &propStorage = prop.builtin;
1239 auto attr = dict.get("builtin");
1240 if (attr || /*isRequired=*/false) {
1241 if (!attr) {
1242 emitError() << "expected key entry for builtin in DictionaryAttr to set "
1243 "Properties.";
1244 return ::mlir::failure();
1245 }
1246 auto convertedAttr = ::llvm::dyn_cast<std::remove_reference_t<decltype(propStorage)>>(attr);
1247 if (convertedAttr) {
1248 propStorage = convertedAttr;
1249 } else {
1250 emitError() << "Invalid attribute `builtin` in property conversion: " << attr;
1251 return ::mlir::failure();
1252 }
1253 }
1254 }
1255
1256 {
1257 auto &propStorage = prop.function;
1258 auto attr = dict.get("function");
1259 if (attr || /*isRequired=*/false) {
1260 if (!attr) {
1261 emitError() << "expected key entry for function in DictionaryAttr to set "
1262 "Properties.";
1263 return ::mlir::failure();
1264 }
1265 auto convertedAttr = ::llvm::dyn_cast<std::remove_reference_t<decltype(propStorage)>>(attr);
1266 if (convertedAttr) {
1267 propStorage = convertedAttr;
1268 } else {
1269 emitError() << "Invalid attribute `function` in property conversion: " << attr;
1270 return ::mlir::failure();
1271 }
1272 }
1273 }
1274
1275 {
1276 auto &propStorage = prop.generic;
1277 auto attr = dict.get("generic");
1278 if (attr || /*isRequired=*/false) {
1279 if (!attr) {
1280 emitError() << "expected key entry for generic in DictionaryAttr to set "
1281 "Properties.";
1282 return ::mlir::failure();
1283 }
1284 auto convertedAttr = ::llvm::dyn_cast<std::remove_reference_t<decltype(propStorage)>>(attr);
1285 if (convertedAttr) {
1286 propStorage = convertedAttr;
1287 } else {
1288 emitError() << "Invalid attribute `generic` in property conversion: " << attr;
1289 return ::mlir::failure();
1290 }
1291 }
1292 }
1293
1294 {
1295 auto &propStorage = prop.params;
1296 auto attr = dict.get("params");
1297 if (attr || /*isRequired=*/false) {
1298 if (!attr) {
1299 emitError() << "expected key entry for params in DictionaryAttr to set "
1300 "Properties.";
1301 return ::mlir::failure();
1302 }
1303 auto convertedAttr = ::llvm::dyn_cast<std::remove_reference_t<decltype(propStorage)>>(attr);
1304 if (convertedAttr) {
1305 propStorage = convertedAttr;
1306 } else {
1307 emitError() << "Invalid attribute `params` in property conversion: " << attr;
1308 return ::mlir::failure();
1309 }
1310 }
1311 }
1312
1313 {
1314 auto &propStorage = prop.sym_name;
1315 auto attr = dict.get("sym_name");
1316 if (attr || /*isRequired=*/true) {
1317 if (!attr) {
1318 emitError() << "expected key entry for sym_name in DictionaryAttr to set "
1319 "Properties.";
1320 return ::mlir::failure();
1321 }
1322 auto convertedAttr = ::llvm::dyn_cast<std::remove_reference_t<decltype(propStorage)>>(attr);
1323 if (convertedAttr) {
1324 propStorage = convertedAttr;
1325 } else {
1326 emitError() << "Invalid attribute `sym_name` in property conversion: " << attr;
1327 return ::mlir::failure();
1328 }
1329 }
1330 }

1352
1353::mlir::Attribute ComponentOp::getPropertiesAsAttr(::mlir::MLIRContext *ctx, const Properties &prop) {
1354 ::mlir::SmallVector<::mlir::NamedAttribute> attrs;
1355 ::mlir::Builder odsBuilder{ctx};
1356
1357 {
1358 const auto &propStorage = prop.builtin;
1359 if (propStorage)
1360 attrs.push_back(odsBuilder.getNamedAttr("builtin",
1361 propStorage));
1362 }
1363
1364 {
1365 const auto &propStorage = prop.function;
1366 if (propStorage)
1367 attrs.push_back(odsBuilder.getNamedAttr("function",
1368 propStorage));
1369 }
1370
1371 {
1372 const auto &propStorage = prop.generic;
1373 if (propStorage)
1374 attrs.push_back(odsBuilder.getNamedAttr("generic",
1375 propStorage));
1376 }
1377
1378 {
1379 const auto &propStorage = prop.params;
1380 if (propStorage)
1381 attrs.push_back(odsBuilder.getNamedAttr("params",
1382 propStorage));
1383 }
1384
1385 {
1386 const auto &propStorage = prop.sym_name;
1387 if (propStorage)
1388 attrs.push_back(odsBuilder.getNamedAttr("sym_name",
1389 propStorage));
1390 }
1391
1392 {
1393 const auto &propStorage = prop.usesBackVariables;
1394 if (propStorage)
1395 attrs.push_back(odsBuilder.getNamedAttr("usesBackVariables",
1396 propStorage));
1397 }
1398
1399 if (!attrs.empty())
1400 return odsBuilder.getDictionaryAttr(attrs);
1401 return {};
1402}
1403
1404llvm::hash_code ComponentOp::computePropertiesHash(const Properties &prop) {
1405 return llvm::hash_combine(
1406 llvm::hash_value(prop.builtin.getAsOpaquePointer()),
1407 llvm::hash_value(prop.function.getAsOpaquePointer()),
1408 llvm::hash_value(prop.generic.getAsOpaquePointer()),
1409 llvm::hash_value(prop.params.getAsOpaquePointer()),
1410 llvm::hash_value(prop.sym_name.getAsOpaquePointer()),
1411 llvm::hash_value(prop.usesBackVariables.getAsOpaquePointer()));
1412}

1414std::optional<mlir::Attribute> ComponentOp::getInherentAttr(::mlir::MLIRContext *ctx, const Properties &prop, llvm::StringRef name) {
1415 if (name == "builtin")
1416 return prop.builtin;
1417
1418 if (name == "function")
1419 return prop.function;
1420
1421 if (name == "generic")
1422 return prop.generic;
1423
1424 if (name == "params")
1425 return prop.params;
1426
1427 if (name == "sym_name")
1428 return prop.sym_name;
1429
1430 if (name == "usesBackVariables")
1431 return prop.usesBackVariables;
1432 return std::nullopt;
1433}
1434
1435void ComponentOp::setInherentAttr(Properties &prop, llvm::StringRef name, mlir::Attribute value) {
1436 if (name == "builtin") {
1437 prop.builtin = ::llvm::dyn_cast_or_null<std::remove_reference_t<decltype(prop.builtin)>>(value);
1438 return;
1439 }
1440
1441 if (name == "function") {
1442 prop.function = ::llvm::dyn_cast_or_null<std::remove_reference_t<decltype(prop.function)>>(value);
1443 return;
1444 }
1445
1446 if (name == "generic") {
1447 prop.generic = ::llvm::dyn_cast_or_null<std::remove_reference_t<decltype(prop.generic)>>(value);
1448 return;
1449 }
1450
1451 if (name == "params") {
1452 prop.params = ::llvm::dyn_cast_or_null<std::remove_reference_t<decltype(prop.params)>>(value);
1453 return;
1454 }
1455
1456 if (name == "sym_name") {
1457 prop.sym_name = ::llvm::dyn_cast_or_null<std::remove_reference_t<decltype(prop.sym_name)>>(value);
1458 return;
1459 }
1460
1461 if (name == "usesBackVariables") {
1462 prop.usesBackVariables = ::llvm::dyn_cast_or_null<std::remove_reference_t<decltype(prop.usesBackVariables)>>(value);
1463 return;
1464 }
1465}

1467void ComponentOp::populateInherentAttrs(::mlir::MLIRContext *ctx, const Properties &prop, ::mlir::NamedAttrList &attrs) {
1468 if (prop.builtin) attrs.append("builtin", prop.builtin);
1469
1470 if (prop.function) attrs.append("function", prop.function);
1471
1472 if (prop.generic) attrs.append("generic", prop.generic);
1473
1474 if (prop.params) attrs.append("params", prop.params);
1475
1476 if (prop.sym_name) attrs.append("sym_name", prop.sym_name);
1477
1478 if (prop.usesBackVariables) attrs.append("usesBackVariables", prop.usesBackVariables);
1479}

1481::mlir::LogicalResult ComponentOp::verifyInherentAttrs(::mlir::OperationName opName, ::mlir::NamedAttrList &attrs, llvm::function_ref<::mlir::InFlightDiagnostic()> emitError) {
1482 {
1483 ::mlir::Attribute attr = attrs.get(getBuiltinAttrName(opName));
1484 if (attr && ::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops1(attr, "builtin", emitError)))
1485 return ::mlir::failure();
1486 }
1487
1488 {
1489 ::mlir::Attribute attr = attrs.get(getFunctionAttrName(opName));
1490 if (attr && ::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops1(attr, "function", emitError)))
1491 return ::mlir::failure();
1492 }
1493
1494 {
1495 ::mlir::Attribute attr = attrs.get(getGenericAttrName(opName));
1496 if (attr && ::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops1(attr, "generic", emitError)))
1497 return ::mlir::failure();
1498 }
1499
1500 {
1501 ::mlir::Attribute attr = attrs.get(getParamsAttrName(opName));
1502 if (attr && ::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops2(attr, "params", emitError)))
1503 return ::mlir::failure();
1504 }
1505
1506 {
1507 ::mlir::Attribute attr = attrs.get(getSymNameAttrName(opName));
1508 if (attr && ::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops0(attr, "sym_name", emitError)))
1509 return ::mlir::failure();
1510 }
1511
1512 {
1513 ::mlir::Attribute attr = attrs.get(getUsesBackVariablesAttrName(opName));
1514 if (attr && ::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops1(attr, "usesBackVariables", emitError)))
1515 return ::mlir::failure();
1516 }
1517 return ::mlir::success();
1518}

1520::mlir::LogicalResult ComponentOp::readProperties(::mlir::DialectBytecodeReader &reader, ::mlir::OperationState &state) {
1521 auto &prop = state.getOrAddProperties<Properties>(); (void)prop;
1522 if (::mlir::failed(reader.readOptionalAttribute(prop.builtin)))
1523 return ::mlir::failure();
1524
1525 if (::mlir::failed(reader.readOptionalAttribute(prop.function)))
1526 return ::mlir::failure();
1527
1528 if (::mlir::failed(reader.readOptionalAttribute(prop.generic)))
1529 return ::mlir::failure();
1530
1531 if (::mlir::failed(reader.readOptionalAttribute(prop.params)))
1532 return ::mlir::failure();
1533
1534 if (::mlir::failed(reader.readAttribute(prop.sym_name)))
1535 return ::mlir::failure();
1536
1537 if (::mlir::failed(reader.readOptionalAttribute(prop.usesBackVariables)))
1538 return ::mlir::failure();
1539 return ::mlir::success();
1540}

1542void ComponentOp::writeProperties(::mlir::DialectBytecodeWriter &writer) {
1543 auto &prop = getProperties(); (void)prop;
1544
1545 writer.writeOptionalAttribute(prop.builtin);
1546
1547 writer.writeOptionalAttribute(prop.function);
1548
1549 writer.writeOptionalAttribute(prop.generic);
1550
1551 writer.writeOptionalAttribute(prop.params);
1552 writer.writeAttribute(prop.sym_name);
1553
1554 writer.writeOptionalAttribute(prop.usesBackVariables);
1555}

1701void ComponentOp::build(::mlir::OpBuilder &odsBuilder, ::mlir::OperationState &odsState, ::mlir::StringAttr sym_name, /*optional*/::mlir::UnitAttr function, /*optional*/::mlir::UnitAttr generic, /*optional*/::mlir::UnitAttr builtin, /*optional*/::mlir::UnitAttr usesBackVariables, /*optional*/::mlir::ArrayAttr params) {
1702 odsState.getOrAddProperties<Properties>().sym_name = sym_name;
1703 if (function) {
1704 odsState.getOrAddProperties<Properties>().function = function;
1705 }
1706 if (generic) {
1707 odsState.getOrAddProperties<Properties>().generic = generic;
1708 }
1709 if (builtin) {
1710 odsState.getOrAddProperties<Properties>().builtin = builtin;
1711 }
1712 if (usesBackVariables) {
1713 odsState.getOrAddProperties<Properties>().usesBackVariables = usesBackVariables;
1714 }
1715 if (params) {
1716 odsState.getOrAddProperties<Properties>().params = params;
1717 }
1718 (void)odsState.addRegion();
1719}
1720
1721void ComponentOp::build(::mlir::OpBuilder &odsBuilder, ::mlir::OperationState &odsState, ::mlir::TypeRange resultTypes, ::mlir::StringAttr sym_name, /*optional*/::mlir::UnitAttr function, /*optional*/::mlir::UnitAttr generic, /*optional*/::mlir::UnitAttr builtin, /*optional*/::mlir::UnitAttr usesBackVariables, /*optional*/::mlir::ArrayAttr params) {
1722 odsState.getOrAddProperties<Properties>().sym_name = sym_name;
1723 if (function) {
1724 odsState.getOrAddProperties<Properties>().function = function;
1725 }
1726 if (generic) {
1727 odsState.getOrAddProperties<Properties>().generic = generic;
1728 }
1729 if (builtin) {
1730 odsState.getOrAddProperties<Properties>().builtin = builtin;
1731 }
1732 if (usesBackVariables) {
1733 odsState.getOrAddProperties<Properties>().usesBackVariables = usesBackVariables;
1734 }
1735 if (params) {
1736 odsState.getOrAddProperties<Properties>().params = params;
1737 }
1738 (void)odsState.addRegion();

1795::mlir::LogicalResult ComponentOp::verifyInvariantsImpl() {
1796 auto tblgen_builtin = getProperties().builtin; (void)tblgen_builtin;
1797 auto tblgen_function = getProperties().function; (void)tblgen_function;
1798 auto tblgen_generic = getProperties().generic; (void)tblgen_generic;
1799 auto tblgen_params = getProperties().params; (void)tblgen_params;
1800 auto tblgen_sym_name = getProperties().sym_name; (void)tblgen_sym_name;
1801 if (!tblgen_sym_name) return emitOpError("requires attribute 'sym_name'");
1802 auto tblgen_usesBackVariables = getProperties().usesBackVariables; (void)tblgen_usesBackVariables;
1803
1804 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops0(*this, tblgen_sym_name, "sym_name")))
1805 return ::mlir::failure();
1806
1807 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops1(*this, tblgen_function, "function")))
1808 return ::mlir::failure();
1809
1810 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops1(*this, tblgen_generic, "generic")))
1811 return ::mlir::failure();
1812
1813 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops1(*this, tblgen_builtin, "builtin")))
1814 return ::mlir::failure();
1815
1816 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops1(*this, tblgen_usesBackVariables, "usesBackVariables")))
1817 return ::mlir::failure();
1818
1819 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops2(*this, tblgen_params, "params")))
1820 return ::mlir::failure();
1821 {
1822 unsigned index = 0; (void)index;
1823
1824 for (auto &region : ::llvm::MutableArrayRef((*this)->getRegion(0)))
1825 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_region_constraint_Ops0(*this, region, "body", index++)))
1826 return ::mlir::failure();
1827 }
1828 return ::mlir::success();
1829}
1830
1831::mlir::LogicalResult ComponentOp::verifyInvariants() {
1832 return verifyInvariantsImpl();
1833}
1834
1835::mlir::ParseResult ComponentOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
1836 ::mlir::StringAttr sym_nameAttr;
1837 ::mlir::ArrayAttr paramsAttr;
1838 std::unique_ptr<::mlir::Region> bodyRegion = std::make_unique<::mlir::Region>();
1839
1840 if (parser.parseSymbolName(sym_nameAttr))
1841 return ::mlir::failure();
1842 if (sym_nameAttr) result.getOrAddProperties<ComponentOp::Properties>().sym_name = sym_nameAttr;
1843 if (::mlir::succeeded(parser.parseOptionalLess())) {
1844
1845 if (parser.parseCustomAttributeWithFallback(paramsAttr, parser.getBuilder().getType<::mlir::NoneType>())) {
1846 return ::mlir::failure();
1847 }
1848 if (paramsAttr) result.getOrAddProperties<ComponentOp::Properties>().params = paramsAttr;
1849 if (parser.parseGreater())
1850 return ::mlir::failure();
1851 }
1852 {
1853 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
1854 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDictWithKeyword(result.attributes))
1855 return ::mlir::failure();
1856 if (failed(verifyInherentAttrs(result.name, result.attributes, [&]() {
1857 return parser.emitError(loc) << "'" << result.name.getStringRef() << "' op ";
1858 })))
1859 return ::mlir::failure();
1860 }
1861
1862 if (parser.parseRegion(*bodyRegion))
1863 return ::mlir::failure();
1864
1865 if (bodyRegion->empty()) bodyRegion->emplaceBlock();
1866 result.addRegion(std::move(bodyRegion));
1867 return ::mlir::success();
1868}
1869
1870void ComponentOp::print(::mlir::OpAsmPrinter &_odsPrinter) {
1871 _odsPrinter << ' ';
1872 _odsPrinter.printSymbolName(getSymNameAttr().getValue());
1873 if (getParamsAttr()) {
1874 _odsPrinter << "<";
1875 _odsPrinter.printAttributeWithoutType(getParamsAttr());
1876 _odsPrinter << ">";
1877 }
1878 ::llvm::SmallVector<::llvm::StringRef, 2> elidedAttrs;
1879 elidedAttrs.push_back("sym_name");
1880 elidedAttrs.push_back("params");
1881 {
1882 ::mlir::Builder odsBuilder(getContext());
1883 ::mlir::Attribute attr = getFunctionAttr();
1884 if(attr && (attr == ((false) ? odsBuilder.getUnitAttr() : nullptr)))
1885 elidedAttrs.push_back("function");
1886 }
1887 {
1888 ::mlir::Builder odsBuilder(getContext());
1889 ::mlir::Attribute attr = getGenericAttr();
1890 if(attr && (attr == ((false) ? odsBuilder.getUnitAttr() : nullptr)))
1891 elidedAttrs.push_back("generic");
1892 }
1893 {
1894 ::mlir::Builder odsBuilder(getContext());
1895 ::mlir::Attribute attr = getBuiltinAttr();
1896 if(attr && (attr == ((false) ? odsBuilder.getUnitAttr() : nullptr)))
1897 elidedAttrs.push_back("builtin");
1898 }
1899 {
1900 ::mlir::Builder odsBuilder(getContext());
1901 ::mlir::Attribute attr = getUsesBackVariablesAttr();
1902 if(attr && (attr == ((false) ? odsBuilder.getUnitAttr() : nullptr)))
1903 elidedAttrs.push_back("usesBackVariables");
1904 }
1905 _odsPrinter.printOptionalAttrDictWithKeyword((*this)->getAttrs(), elidedAttrs);
1906 _odsPrinter << ' ';
1907 _odsPrinter.printRegion(getBody());
1908}

1920ConstrainCallOpGenericAdaptorBase::ConstrainCallOpGenericAdaptorBase(::mlir::DictionaryAttr attrs, const ::mlir::EmptyProperties &properties, ::mlir::RegionRange regions) : odsAttrs(attrs), odsRegions(regions) { if (odsAttrs)

1925
1926std::pair<unsigned, unsigned> ConstrainCallOpGenericAdaptorBase::getODSOperandIndexAndLength(unsigned index, unsigned odsOperandsSize) {
1927 bool isVariadic[] = {false, true};
1928 int prevVariadicCount = 0;
1929 for (unsigned i = 0; i < index; ++i)
1930 if (isVariadic[i]) ++prevVariadicCount;
1931
1932 // Calculate how many dynamic values a static variadic operand corresponds to.
1933 // This assumes all static variadic operands have the same dynamic value count.
1934 int variadicSize = (odsOperandsSize - 1) / 1;
1935 // `index` passed in as the parameter is the static index which counts each
1936 // operand (variadic or not) as size 1. So here for each previous static variadic
1937 // operand, we need to offset by (variadicSize - 1) to get where the dynamic
1938 // value pack for this static operand starts.
1939 int start = index + (variadicSize - 1) * prevVariadicCount;
1940 int size = isVariadic[index] ? variadicSize : 1;
1941 return {start, size};
1942}

1945 return odsAttrs;
1946}

1962 // This assumes all static variadic operands have the same dynamic value count.

2051::mlir::ParseResult ConstrainCallOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
2052 ::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand selfRawOperands[1];
2053 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand> selfOperands(selfRawOperands); ::llvm::SMLoc selfOperandsLoc;
2054 (void)selfOperandsLoc;
2055 ::llvm::SmallVector<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand, 4> argsOperands;
2056 ::llvm::SMLoc argsOperandsLoc;
2057 (void)argsOperandsLoc;
2058 ::mlir::Type selfRawTypes[1];
2059 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> selfTypes(selfRawTypes);
2060 ::llvm::SmallVector<::mlir::Type, 1> argsTypes;
2061
2062 selfOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
2063 if (parser.parseOperand(selfRawOperands[0]))
2064 return ::mlir::failure();
2065 if (parser.parseLParen())
2066 return ::mlir::failure();
2067
2068 argsOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
2069 if (parser.parseOperandList(argsOperands))
2070 return ::mlir::failure();
2071 if (parser.parseRParen())
2072 return ::mlir::failure();
2073 if (parser.parseColon())
2074 return ::mlir::failure();
2075
2076 {
2077 ::mlir::Type type;
2078 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
2079 return ::mlir::failure();
2080 selfRawTypes[0] = type;
2081 }
2082 if (::mlir::succeeded(parser.parseOptionalComma())) {
2083
2084 if (parser.parseTypeList(argsTypes))
2085 return ::mlir::failure();
2086 }
2087 {
2088 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
2089 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
2090 return ::mlir::failure();
2091 }
2092 if (parser.resolveOperands(selfOperands, selfTypes, selfOperandsLoc, result.operands))
2093 return ::mlir::failure();
2094 if (parser.resolveOperands(argsOperands, argsTypes, argsOperandsLoc, result.operands))
2095 return ::mlir::failure();
2096 return ::mlir::success();
2097}

2235::mlir::ParseResult ConstrainOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
2236 ::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand lhsRawOperands[1];
2237 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand> lhsOperands(lhsRawOperands); ::llvm::SMLoc lhsOperandsLoc;
2238 (void)lhsOperandsLoc;
2239 ::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand rhsRawOperands[1];
2240 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand> rhsOperands(rhsRawOperands); ::llvm::SMLoc rhsOperandsLoc;
2241 (void)rhsOperandsLoc;
2242 ::mlir::Type lhsRawTypes[1];
2243 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> lhsTypes(lhsRawTypes);
2244 ::mlir::Type rhsRawTypes[1];
2245 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> rhsTypes(rhsRawTypes);
2246
2247 lhsOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
2248 if (parser.parseOperand(lhsRawOperands[0]))
2249 return ::mlir::failure();
2250 if (parser.parseEqual())
2251 return ::mlir::failure();
2252
2253 rhsOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
2254 if (parser.parseOperand(rhsRawOperands[0]))
2255 return ::mlir::failure();
2256 {
2257 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
2258 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
2259 return ::mlir::failure();
2260 }
2261 if (parser.parseColon())
2262 return ::mlir::failure();
2263
2264 {
2265 ::mlir::Type type;
2266 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
2267 return ::mlir::failure();
2268 lhsRawTypes[0] = type;
2269 }
2270 if (parser.parseComma())
2271 return ::mlir::failure();
2272
2273 {
2274 ::mlir::Type type;
2275 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
2276 return ::mlir::failure();
2277 rhsRawTypes[0] = type;
2278 }
2279 if (parser.resolveOperands(lhsOperands, lhsTypes, lhsOperandsLoc, result.operands))
2280 return ::mlir::failure();
2281 if (parser.resolveOperands(rhsOperands, rhsTypes, rhsOperandsLoc, result.operands))
2282 return ::mlir::failure();
2283 return ::mlir::success();
2284}
2285
2286void ConstrainOp::print(::mlir::OpAsmPrinter &_odsPrinter) {
2287 _odsPrinter << ' ';
2288 _odsPrinter << getLhs();
2289 _odsPrinter << ' ' << "=";
2290 _odsPrinter << ' ';
2291 _odsPrinter << getRhs();
2292 ::llvm::SmallVector<::llvm::StringRef, 2> elidedAttrs;
2293 _odsPrinter.printOptionalAttrDict((*this)->getAttrs(), elidedAttrs);
2294 _odsPrinter << ' ' << ":";
2295 _odsPrinter << ' ';
2296 {
2297 auto type = getLhs().getType();
2298 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::mlir::Type>(type))
2299 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
2300 else
2301 _odsPrinter << type;
2302 }
2303 _odsPrinter << ",";
2304 _odsPrinter << ' ';
2305 {
2306 auto type = getRhs().getType();
2307 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::mlir::Type>(type))
2308 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
2309 else
2310 _odsPrinter << type;
2311 }
2312}

2375::mlir::LogicalResult ConstructorRefOpAdaptor::verify(::mlir::Location loc) {
2376 auto tblgen_builtin = getProperties().builtin; (void)tblgen_builtin;
2377 auto tblgen_component = getProperties().component; (void)tblgen_component;
2378 if (!tblgen_component) return emitError(loc, "'zml.constructor' op ""requires attribute 'component'");
2379 auto tblgen_numLiftedParams = getProperties().numLiftedParams; (void)tblgen_numLiftedParams;
2380 if (!tblgen_numLiftedParams) return emitError(loc, "'zml.constructor' op ""requires attribute 'numLiftedParams'");
2381
2382 if (tblgen_component && !((::llvm::isa<::mlir::FlatSymbolRefAttr>(tblgen_component))))
2383 return emitError(loc, "'zml.constructor' op ""attribute 'component' failed to satisfy constraint: flat symbol reference attribute");
2384
2385 if (tblgen_numLiftedParams && !(((::llvm::isa<::mlir::IntegerAttr>(tblgen_numLiftedParams))) && ((::llvm::isa<::mlir::IndexType>(::llvm::cast<::mlir::IntegerAttr>(tblgen_numLiftedParams).getType())))))
2386 return emitError(loc, "'zml.constructor' op ""attribute 'numLiftedParams' failed to satisfy constraint: index attribute");
2387
2388 if (tblgen_builtin && !((::llvm::isa<::mlir::UnitAttr>(tblgen_builtin))))
2389 return emitError(loc, "'zml.constructor' op ""attribute 'builtin' failed to satisfy constraint: unit attribute");
2390 return ::mlir::success();
2391}

2430 if (convertedAttr) {
2431 propStorage = convertedAttr;
2432 } else {
2433 emitError() << "Invalid attribute `builtin` in property conversion: " << attr;
2434 return ::mlir::failure();
2435 }
2436 }
2437 }
2438

2440 auto &propStorage = prop.component;
2441 auto attr = dict.get("component");
2442 if (attr || /*isRequired=*/true) {
2443 if (!attr) {

2445 "Properties.";
2446 return ::mlir::failure();
2447 }
2448 auto convertedAttr = ::llvm::dyn_cast<std::remove_reference_t<decltype(propStorage)>>(attr);
2449 if (convertedAttr) {
2450 propStorage = convertedAttr;
2451 } else {
2452 emitError() << "Invalid attribute `component` in property conversion: " << attr;
2453 return ::mlir::failure();
2454 }
2455 }
2456 }
2457
2458 {
2459 auto &propStorage = prop.numLiftedParams;
2460 auto attr = dict.get("numLiftedParams");
2461 if (attr || /*isRequired=*/true) {
2462 if (!attr) {

2464 "Properties.";

2553::mlir::LogicalResult ConstructorRefOp::verifyInherentAttrs(::mlir::OperationName opName, ::mlir::NamedAttrList &attrs, llvm::function_ref<::mlir::InFlightDiagnostic()> emitError) {
2554 {
2555 ::mlir::Attribute attr = attrs.get(getBuiltinAttrName(opName));
2556 if (attr && ::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops1(attr, "builtin", emitError)))
2557 return ::mlir::failure();
2558 }
2559
2560 {
2561 ::mlir::Attribute attr = attrs.get(getComponentAttrName(opName));
2562 if (attr && ::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops3(attr, "component", emitError)))
2563 return ::mlir::failure();
2564 }
2565
2566 {
2567 ::mlir::Attribute attr = attrs.get(getNumLiftedParamsAttrName(opName));
2568 if (attr && ::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops4(attr, "numLiftedParams", emitError)))
2569 return ::mlir::failure();
2570 }
2571 return ::mlir::success();
2572}

2666::mlir::LogicalResult ConstructorRefOp::verifyInvariantsImpl() {
2667 auto tblgen_builtin = getProperties().builtin; (void)tblgen_builtin;
2668 auto tblgen_component = getProperties().component; (void)tblgen_component;
2669 if (!tblgen_component) return emitOpError("requires attribute 'component'");
2670 auto tblgen_numLiftedParams = getProperties().numLiftedParams; (void)tblgen_numLiftedParams;
2671 if (!tblgen_numLiftedParams) return emitOpError("requires attribute 'numLiftedParams'");
2672
2673 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops3(*this, tblgen_component, "component")))
2674 return ::mlir::failure();
2675
2676 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops4(*this, tblgen_numLiftedParams, "numLiftedParams")))
2677 return ::mlir::failure();
2678
2679 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops1(*this, tblgen_builtin, "builtin")))
2680 return ::mlir::failure();
2681 {
2682 unsigned index = 0; (void)index;
2683 auto valueGroup0 = getODSResults(0);
2684
2685 for (auto v : valueGroup0) {
2686 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_type_constraint_Ops4(*this, v.getType(), "result", index++)))
2687 return ::mlir::failure();
2688 }
2689 }
2690 return ::mlir::success();
2691}
2692
2693::mlir::LogicalResult ConstructorRefOp::verifyInvariants() {
2694 if(::mlir::succeeded(verifyInvariantsImpl()) && ::mlir::succeeded(verify()))
2695 return ::mlir::success();
2696 return ::mlir::failure();
2697}
2698
2699::mlir::ParseResult ConstructorRefOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
2700 ::mlir::FlatSymbolRefAttr componentAttr;
2701 ::llvm::SmallVector<::mlir::Type, 1> allResultTypes;
2702 {
2703 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
2704 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
2705 return ::mlir::failure();
2706 if (failed(verifyInherentAttrs(result.name, result.attributes, [&]() {
2707 return parser.emitError(loc) << "'" << result.name.getStringRef() << "' op ";
2708 })))
2709 return ::mlir::failure();
2710 }
2711
2712 if (parser.parseCustomAttributeWithFallback(componentAttr, parser.getBuilder().getType<::mlir::NoneType>())) {
2713 return ::mlir::failure();
2714 }
2715 if (componentAttr) result.getOrAddProperties<ConstructorRefOp::Properties>().component = componentAttr;
2716 if (parser.parseColon())
2717 return ::mlir::failure();
2718
2719 if (parser.parseTypeList(allResultTypes))
2720 return ::mlir::failure();
2721 result.addTypes(allResultTypes);
2722 return ::mlir::success();
2723}
2724
2725void ConstructorRefOp::print(::mlir::OpAsmPrinter &_odsPrinter) {
2726 ::llvm::SmallVector<::llvm::StringRef, 2> elidedAttrs;
2727 elidedAttrs.push_back("component");
2728 {
2729 ::mlir::Builder odsBuilder(getContext());
2730 ::mlir::Attribute attr = getBuiltinAttr();
2731 if(attr && (attr == ((false) ? odsBuilder.getUnitAttr() : nullptr)))
2732 elidedAttrs.push_back("builtin");
2733 }
2734 _odsPrinter.printOptionalAttrDict((*this)->getAttrs(), elidedAttrs);
2735 _odsPrinter << ' ';
2736 _odsPrinter.printAttributeWithoutType(getComponentAttr());
2737 _odsPrinter << ' ' << ":";
2738 _odsPrinter << ' ';
2739 _odsPrinter << getOperation()->getResultTypes();
2740}

2823::mlir::LogicalResult EqzExtOp::verifyInvariantsImpl() {
2824 {
2825 unsigned index = 0; (void)index;
2826 auto valueGroup0 = getODSOperands(0);

3383 odsState.addTypes(resultTypes);

3418::mlir::ParseResult ExtMulOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
3419 ::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand lhsRawOperands[1];
3420 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand> lhsOperands(lhsRawOperands); ::llvm::SMLoc lhsOperandsLoc;
3421 (void)lhsOperandsLoc;
3422 ::mlir::Type lhsRawTypes[1];
3423 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> lhsTypes(lhsRawTypes);
3424 ::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand rhsRawOperands[1];
3425 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand> rhsOperands(rhsRawOperands); ::llvm::SMLoc rhsOperandsLoc;
3426 (void)rhsOperandsLoc;
3427 ::mlir::Type rhsRawTypes[1];
3428 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> rhsTypes(rhsRawTypes);
3429 ::mlir::Type outRawTypes[1];
3430 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> outTypes(outRawTypes);
3431
3432 lhsOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
3433 if (parser.parseOperand(lhsRawOperands[0]))
3434 return ::mlir::failure();
3435 if (parser.parseColon())
3436 return ::mlir::failure();
3437
3438 {
3439 ::zml::ComponentType type;
3440 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
3441 return ::mlir::failure();
3442 lhsRawTypes[0] = type;
3443 }
3444 if (parser.parseComma())
3445 return ::mlir::failure();
3446
3447 rhsOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
3448 if (parser.parseOperand(rhsRawOperands[0]))
3449 return ::mlir::failure();
3450 if (parser.parseColon())
3451 return ::mlir::failure();
3452
3453 {
3454 ::zml::ComponentType type;
3455 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
3456 return ::mlir::failure();
3457 rhsRawTypes[0] = type;
3458 }
3459 if (parser.parseArrow())
3460 return ::mlir::failure();
3461
3462 {
3463 ::zml::ComponentType type;
3464 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
3465 return ::mlir::failure();
3466 outRawTypes[0] = type;
3467 }
3468 {
3469 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
3470 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
3471 return ::mlir::failure();
3472 }
3473 result.addTypes(outTypes);
3474 if (parser.resolveOperands(lhsOperands, lhsTypes, lhsOperandsLoc, result.operands))
3475 return ::mlir::failure();
3476 if (parser.resolveOperands(rhsOperands, rhsTypes, rhsOperandsLoc, result.operands))
3477 return ::mlir::failure();
3478 return ::mlir::success();
3479}

3486 {

3488 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::zml::ComponentType>(type))
3489 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
3490 else
3491 _odsPrinter << type;
3492 }
3493 _odsPrinter << ",";
3494 _odsPrinter << ' ';
3495 _odsPrinter << getRhs();
3496 _odsPrinter << ' ' << ":";
3497 _odsPrinter << ' ';
3498 {
3499 auto type = getRhs().getType();
3500 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::zml::ComponentType>(type))
3501 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
3502 else
3503 _odsPrinter << type;
3504 }
3505 _odsPrinter << ' ' << "->";
3506 _odsPrinter << ' ';
3507 {
3508 auto type = getOut().getType();
3509 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::zml::ComponentType>(type))
3510 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
3511 else
3512 _odsPrinter << type;
3513 }

3515 _odsPrinter.printOptionalAttrDict((*this)->getAttrs(), elidedAttrs);

3816::mlir::LogicalResult ExternFnRefOp::setPropertiesFromAttr(Properties &prop, ::mlir::Attribute attr, ::llvm::function_ref<::mlir::InFlightDiagnostic()> emitError) {
3817 ::mlir::DictionaryAttr dict = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::mlir::DictionaryAttr>(attr);
3818 if (!dict) {
3819 emitError() << "expected DictionaryAttr to set properties";
3820 return ::mlir::failure();
3821 }
3822
3823 {
3824 auto &propStorage = prop.name;
3825 auto attr = dict.get("name");
3826 if (attr || /*isRequired=*/true) {
3827 if (!attr) {
3828 emitError() << "expected key entry for name in DictionaryAttr to set "
3829 "Properties.";
3830 return ::mlir::failure();
3831 }
3832 auto convertedAttr = ::llvm::dyn_cast<std::remove_reference_t<decltype(propStorage)>>(attr);
3833 if (convertedAttr) {
3834 propStorage = convertedAttr;
3835 } else {
3836 emitError() << "Invalid attribute `name` in property conversion: " << attr;
3837 return ::mlir::failure();
3838 }
3839 }
3840 }
3841 return ::mlir::success();
3842}

3940}

3943 assert(operands.size() == 0u && "mismatched number of parameters");

3950::mlir::LogicalResult ExternFnRefOp::verifyInvariantsImpl() {
3951 auto tblgen_name = getProperties().name; (void)tblgen_name;
3952 if (!tblgen_name) return emitOpError("requires attribute 'name'");
3953
3954 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops3(*this, tblgen_name, "name")))
3955 return ::mlir::failure();
3956 {
3957 unsigned index = 0; (void)index;
3958 auto valueGroup0 = getODSResults(0);
3959
3960 for (auto v : valueGroup0) {
3961 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_type_constraint_Ops4(*this, v.getType(), "result", index++)))
3962 return ::mlir::failure();
3963 }
3964 }
3965 return ::mlir::success();

3972::mlir::ParseResult ExternFnRefOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
3973 ::mlir::FlatSymbolRefAttr nameAttr;
3974 ::llvm::SmallVector<::mlir::Type, 1> allResultTypes;
3975 {
3976 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
3977 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
3978 return ::mlir::failure();
3979 if (failed(verifyInherentAttrs(result.name, result.attributes, [&]() {
3980 return parser.emitError(loc) << "'" << result.name.getStringRef() << "' op ";
3981 })))
3982 return ::mlir::failure();
3983 }
3984
3985 if (parser.parseCustomAttributeWithFallback(nameAttr, parser.getBuilder().getType<::mlir::NoneType>())) {
3986 return ::mlir::failure();
3987 }
3988 if (nameAttr) result.getOrAddProperties<ExternFnRefOp::Properties>().name = nameAttr;
3989 if (parser.parseColon())
3990 return ::mlir::failure();
3991
3992 if (parser.parseTypeList(allResultTypes))
3993 return ::mlir::failure();
3994 result.addTypes(allResultTypes);
3995 return ::mlir::success();
3996}

3998void ExternFnRefOp::print(::mlir::OpAsmPrinter &_odsPrinter) {
3999 ::llvm::SmallVector<::llvm::StringRef, 2> elidedAttrs;
4000 elidedAttrs.push_back("name");
4001 _odsPrinter.printOptionalAttrDict((*this)->getAttrs(), elidedAttrs);
4002 _odsPrinter << ' ';
4003 _odsPrinter.printAttributeWithoutType(getNameAttr());
4004 _odsPrinter << ' ' << ":";
4005 _odsPrinter << ' ';
4006 _odsPrinter << getOperation()->getResultTypes();

4073::mlir::LogicalResult FieldDefOpAdaptor::verify(::mlir::Location loc) {
4074 auto tblgen_column = getProperties().column; (void)tblgen_column;
4075 auto tblgen_sym_name = getProperties().sym_name; (void)tblgen_sym_name;
4076 if (!tblgen_sym_name) return emitError(loc, "'zml.field' op ""requires attribute 'sym_name'");
4077 auto tblgen_type = getProperties().type; (void)tblgen_type;
4078 if (!tblgen_type) return emitError(loc, "'zml.field' op ""requires attribute 'type'");
4079
4080 if (tblgen_sym_name && !((::llvm::isa<::mlir::StringAttr>(tblgen_sym_name))))
4081 return emitError(loc, "'zml.field' op ""attribute 'sym_name' failed to satisfy constraint: string attribute");
4082
4083 if (tblgen_type && !(((::llvm::isa<::mlir::TypeAttr>(tblgen_type))) && ((::llvm::isa<::mlir::Type>(::llvm::cast<::mlir::TypeAttr>(tblgen_type).getValue()))) && (((::llvm::isa<::zml::ComponentType>(::llvm::cast<::mlir::TypeAttr>(tblgen_type).getValue()))) || ((::llvm::isa<::zml::TypeVarType>(::llvm::cast<::mlir::TypeAttr>(tblgen_type).getValue()))))))
4084 return emitError(loc, "'zml.field' op ""attribute 'type' failed to satisfy constraint: type attribute of component type or parametric type");
4085
4086 if (tblgen_column && !((::llvm::isa<::mlir::UnitAttr>(tblgen_column))))
4087 return emitError(loc, "'zml.field' op ""attribute 'column' failed to satisfy constraint: unit attribute");
4088 return ::mlir::success();
4089}

4420::mlir::ParseResult FieldDefOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
4421 ::mlir::StringAttr sym_nameAttr;
4422 ::mlir::TypeAttr typeAttr;
4423
4424 if (parser.parseSymbolName(sym_nameAttr))
4425 return ::mlir::failure();
4426 if (sym_nameAttr) result.getOrAddProperties<FieldDefOp::Properties>().sym_name = sym_nameAttr;
4427 if (parser.parseColon())
4428 return ::mlir::failure();
4429
4430 if (parser.parseCustomAttributeWithFallback(typeAttr, parser.getBuilder().getType<::mlir::NoneType>())) {
4431 return ::mlir::failure();
4432 }
4433 if (typeAttr) result.getOrAddProperties<FieldDefOp::Properties>().type = typeAttr;
4434 {
4435 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
4436 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
4437 return ::mlir::failure();
4438 if (failed(verifyInherentAttrs(result.name, result.attributes, [&]() {
4439 return parser.emitError(loc) << "'" << result.name.getStringRef() << "' op ";
4440 })))
4441 return ::mlir::failure();
4442 }
4443 return ::mlir::success();

4446void FieldDefOp::print(::mlir::OpAsmPrinter &_odsPrinter) {
4447 _odsPrinter << ' ';
4448 _odsPrinter.printSymbolName(getSymNameAttr().getValue());
4449 _odsPrinter << ' ' << ":";
4450 _odsPrinter << ' ';
4451 _odsPrinter.printAttributeWithoutType(getTypeAttr());
4452 ::llvm::SmallVector<::llvm::StringRef, 2> elidedAttrs;
4453 elidedAttrs.push_back("sym_name");
4454 elidedAttrs.push_back("type");
4455 {
4456 ::mlir::Builder odsBuilder(getContext());
4457 ::mlir::Attribute attr = getColumnAttr();
4458 if(attr && (attr == ((false) ? odsBuilder.getUnitAttr() : nullptr)))
4459 elidedAttrs.push_back("column");
4460 }
4461 _odsPrinter.printOptionalAttrDict((*this)->getAttrs(), elidedAttrs);
4462}

4613::mlir::ParseResult GetArrayLenOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
4614 ::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand arrayRawOperands[1];
4615 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand> arrayOperands(arrayRawOperands); ::llvm::SMLoc arrayOperandsLoc;
4616 (void)arrayOperandsLoc;
4617 ::mlir::Type arrayRawTypes[1];
4618 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> arrayTypes(arrayRawTypes);
4619
4620 arrayOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
4621 if (parser.parseOperand(arrayRawOperands[0]))
4622 return ::mlir::failure();
4623 {
4624 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
4625 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
4626 return ::mlir::failure();
4627 }
4628 if (parser.parseColon())
4629 return ::mlir::failure();
4630
4631 {
4632 ::mlir::Type type;
4633 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
4634 return ::mlir::failure();
4635 arrayRawTypes[0] = type;
4636 }
4637 ::mlir::Type odsBuildableType0 = parser.getBuilder().getIndexType();
4638 result.addTypes(odsBuildableType0);
4639 if (parser.resolveOperands(arrayOperands, arrayTypes, arrayOperandsLoc, result.operands))
4640 return ::mlir::failure();
4641 return ::mlir::success();

5015 emitError() << "expected key entry for sym_name in DictionaryAttr to set "
5016 "Properties.";
5017 return ::mlir::failure();
5018 }
5019 auto convertedAttr = ::llvm::dyn_cast<std::remove_reference_t<decltype(propStorage)>>(attr);
5020 if (convertedAttr) {
5021 propStorage = convertedAttr;
5022 } else {
5023 emitError() << "Invalid attribute `sym_name` in property conversion: " << attr;
5024 return ::mlir::failure();
5025 }
5026 }
5027 }
5028
5029 {
5030 auto &propStorage = prop.type;
5031 auto attr = dict.get("type");
5032 if (attr || /*isRequired=*/true) {
5033 if (!attr) {
5034 emitError() << "expected key entry for type in DictionaryAttr to set "
5035 "Properties.";
5036 return ::mlir::failure();
5037 }
5038 auto convertedAttr = ::llvm::dyn_cast<std::remove_reference_t<decltype(propStorage)>>(attr);
5039 if (convertedAttr) {
5040 propStorage = convertedAttr;
5041 } else {
5042 emitError() << "Invalid attribute `type` in property conversion: " << attr;
5043 return ::mlir::failure();
5044 }
5045 }
5046 }
5047 return ::mlir::success();
5048}

5050::mlir::Attribute GlobalDefOp::getPropertiesAsAttr(::mlir::MLIRContext *ctx, const Properties &prop) {
5051 ::mlir::SmallVector<::mlir::NamedAttribute> attrs;
5052 ::mlir::Builder odsBuilder{ctx};
5053
5054 {
5055 const auto &propStorage = prop.sym_name;
5056 if (propStorage)
5057 attrs.push_back(odsBuilder.getNamedAttr("sym_name",
5058 propStorage));
5059 }
5060
5061 {
5062 const auto &propStorage = prop.type;
5063 if (propStorage)
5064 attrs.push_back(odsBuilder.getNamedAttr("type",
5065 propStorage));
5066 }
5067
5068 if (!attrs.empty())
5069 return odsBuilder.getDictionaryAttr(attrs);
5070 return {};
5071}

5076 llvm::hash_value(prop.type.getAsOpaquePointer()));

5203::mlir::LogicalResult GlobalDefOp::verifyInvariantsImpl() {
5204 auto tblgen_sym_name = getProperties().sym_name; (void)tblgen_sym_name;
5205 if (!tblgen_sym_name) return emitOpError("requires attribute 'sym_name'");
5206 auto tblgen_type = getProperties().type; (void)tblgen_type;
5207 if (!tblgen_type) return emitOpError("requires attribute 'type'");
5208
5209 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops0(*this, tblgen_sym_name, "sym_name")))
5210 return ::mlir::failure();
5211
5212 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops7(*this, tblgen_type, "type")))
5213 return ::mlir::failure();
5214 return ::mlir::success();
5215}
5216
5217::mlir::LogicalResult GlobalDefOp::verifyInvariants() {
5218 return verifyInvariantsImpl();
5219}

5221::mlir::ParseResult GlobalDefOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
5222 ::mlir::StringAttr sym_nameAttr;
5223 ::mlir::TypeAttr typeAttr;
5224
5225 if (parser.parseSymbolName(sym_nameAttr))
5226 return ::mlir::failure();
5227 if (sym_nameAttr) result.getOrAddProperties<GlobalDefOp::Properties>().sym_name = sym_nameAttr;
5228 if (parser.parseColon())
5229 return ::mlir::failure();
5230
5231 if (parser.parseCustomAttributeWithFallback(typeAttr, parser.getBuilder().getType<::mlir::NoneType>())) {
5232 return ::mlir::failure();
5233 }
5234 if (typeAttr) result.getOrAddProperties<GlobalDefOp::Properties>().type = typeAttr;
5235 {
5236 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
5237 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
5238 return ::mlir::failure();
5239 if (failed(verifyInherentAttrs(result.name, result.attributes, [&]() {
5240 return parser.emitError(loc) << "'" << result.name.getStringRef() << "' op ";
5241 })))
5242 return ::mlir::failure();
5243 }
5244 return ::mlir::success();
5245}

5247void GlobalDefOp::print(::mlir::OpAsmPrinter &_odsPrinter) {
5248 _odsPrinter << ' ';
5249 _odsPrinter.printSymbolName(getSymNameAttr().getValue());
5250 _odsPrinter << ' ' << ":";
5251 _odsPrinter << ' ';
5252 _odsPrinter.printAttributeWithoutType(getTypeAttr());
5253 ::llvm::SmallVector<::llvm::StringRef, 2> elidedAttrs;
5254 elidedAttrs.push_back("sym_name");
5255 elidedAttrs.push_back("type");
5256 _odsPrinter.printOptionalAttrDict((*this)->getAttrs(), elidedAttrs);
5257}

5401
5402::mlir::ParseResult InRangeOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
5403 ::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand lowRawOperands[1];
5404 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand> lowOperands(lowRawOperands); ::llvm::SMLoc lowOperandsLoc;
5405 (void)lowOperandsLoc;
5406 ::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand midRawOperands[1];
5407 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand> midOperands(midRawOperands); ::llvm::SMLoc midOperandsLoc;
5408 (void)midOperandsLoc;
5409 ::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand highRawOperands[1];
5410 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand> highOperands(highRawOperands); ::llvm::SMLoc highOperandsLoc;
5411 (void)highOperandsLoc;
5412 ::mlir::Type lowRawTypes[1];
5413 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> lowTypes(lowRawTypes);
5414 ::mlir::Type midRawTypes[1];
5415 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> midTypes(midRawTypes);
5416 ::mlir::Type highRawTypes[1];
5417 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> highTypes(highRawTypes);
5418 ::mlir::Type outRawTypes[1];
5419 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> outTypes(outRawTypes);
5420
5421 lowOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
5422 if (parser.parseOperand(lowRawOperands[0]))
5423 return ::mlir::failure();
5424 if (parser.parseLess())
5425 return ::mlir::failure();
5426 if (parser.parseEqual())
5427 return ::mlir::failure();
5428
5429 midOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
5430 if (parser.parseOperand(midRawOperands[0]))
5431 return ::mlir::failure();
5432 if (parser.parseLess())
5433 return ::mlir::failure();
5434
5435 highOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
5436 if (parser.parseOperand(highRawOperands[0]))
5437 return ::mlir::failure();
5438 if (parser.parseColon())
5439 return ::mlir::failure();
5440 if (parser.parseLParen())
5441 return ::mlir::failure();
5442
5443 {
5444 ::zml::ComponentType type;
5445 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
5446 return ::mlir::failure();
5447 lowRawTypes[0] = type;
5448 }
5449 if (parser.parseComma())
5450 return ::mlir::failure();
5451
5452 {
5453 ::zml::ComponentType type;
5454 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
5455 return ::mlir::failure();
5456 midRawTypes[0] = type;
5457 }
5458 if (parser.parseComma())
5459 return ::mlir::failure();
5460
5461 {
5462 ::zml::ComponentType type;
5463 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
5464 return ::mlir::failure();
5465 highRawTypes[0] = type;
5466 }
5467 if (parser.parseRParen())
5468 return ::mlir::failure();
5469 if (parser.parseArrow())
5470 return ::mlir::failure();
5471
5472 {
5473 ::zml::ComponentType type;
5474 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
5475 return ::mlir::failure();
5476 outRawTypes[0] = type;
5477 }
5478 {
5479 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
5480 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
5481 return ::mlir::failure();
5482 }
5483 result.addTypes(outTypes);
5484 if (parser.resolveOperands(lowOperands, lowTypes, lowOperandsLoc, result.operands))
5485 return ::mlir::failure();
5486 if (parser.resolveOperands(midOperands, midTypes, midOperandsLoc, result.operands))
5487 return ::mlir::failure();
5488 if (parser.resolveOperands(highOperands, highTypes, highOperandsLoc, result.operands))
5489 return ::mlir::failure();
5490 return ::mlir::success();
5491}

5494 _odsPrinter << ' ';
5495 _odsPrinter << getLow();
5496 _odsPrinter << ' ';
5497 _odsPrinter << "<";
5498 _odsPrinter << "=";

5500 _odsPrinter << getMid();
5501 _odsPrinter << ' ';
5502 _odsPrinter << "<";
5503 _odsPrinter << ' ';
5504 _odsPrinter << ' ';
5505 _odsPrinter << getHigh();
5506 _odsPrinter << ' ' << ":";
5507 _odsPrinter << ' ' << "(";

5510 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::zml::ComponentType>(type))
5511 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
5512 else

5521 else

5528 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::zml::ComponentType>(type))
5529 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
5530 else
5531 _odsPrinter << type;
5532 }
5533 _odsPrinter << ")";
5534 _odsPrinter << ' ' << "->";

5539 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
5540 else
5541 _odsPrinter << type;

5662 (void)indexOperandsLoc;

5669 if (parser.parseColon())

5681 return ::mlir::failure();

5683 ::mlir::Type odsBuildableType0 = parser.getBuilder().getIndexType();
5684 result.addTypes(resultTypes);
5685 if (parser.resolveOperands(indexOperands, odsBuildableType0, indexOperandsLoc, result.operands))
5686 return ::mlir::failure();

6135::mlir::LogicalResult LitStrOp::setPropertiesFromAttr(Properties &prop, ::mlir::Attribute attr, ::llvm::function_ref<::mlir::InFlightDiagnostic()> emitError) {
6136 ::mlir::DictionaryAttr dict = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::mlir::DictionaryAttr>(attr);
6137 if (!dict) {
6138 emitError() << "expected DictionaryAttr to set properties";
6139 return ::mlir::failure();
6140 }
6141
6142 {
6143 auto &propStorage = prop.value;
6144 auto attr = dict.get("value");
6145 if (attr || /*isRequired=*/true) {
6146 if (!attr) {
6147 emitError() << "expected key entry for value in DictionaryAttr to set "
6148 "Properties.";
6149 return ::mlir::failure();
6150 }
6151 auto convertedAttr = ::llvm::dyn_cast<std::remove_reference_t<decltype(propStorage)>>(attr);
6152 if (convertedAttr) {
6153 propStorage = convertedAttr;
6154 } else {
6155 emitError() << "Invalid attribute `value` in property conversion: " << attr;
6156 return ::mlir::failure();
6157 }
6158 }
6159 }
6160 return ::mlir::success();
6161}

6169 if (propStorage)

6171 propStorage));

6174 if (!attrs.empty())
6175 return odsBuilder.getDictionaryAttr(attrs);
6176 return {};

6269::mlir::LogicalResult LitStrOp::verifyInvariantsImpl() {
6270 auto tblgen_value = getProperties().value; (void)tblgen_value;
6271 if (!tblgen_value) return emitOpError("requires attribute 'value'");
6272
6273 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops0(*this, tblgen_value, "value")))
6274 return ::mlir::failure();
6275 {
6276 unsigned index = 0; (void)index;
6277 auto valueGroup0 = getODSResults(0);
6278
6279 for (auto v : valueGroup0) {
6280 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_type_constraint_Ops0(*this, v.getType(), "result", index++)))
6281 return ::mlir::failure();
6282 }
6283 }
6284 return ::mlir::success();
6285}

6287::mlir::LogicalResult LitStrOp::verifyInvariants() {
6288 return verifyInvariantsImpl();

6290
6291::mlir::ParseResult LitStrOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
6292 ::mlir::StringAttr valueAttr;
6293 ::mlir::Type valRawTypes[1];
6294 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> valTypes(valRawTypes);
6295
6296 if (parser.parseCustomAttributeWithFallback(valueAttr, parser.getBuilder().getType<::mlir::NoneType>())) {
6297 return ::mlir::failure();
6298 }
6299 if (valueAttr) result.getOrAddProperties<LitStrOp::Properties>().value = valueAttr;
6300 if (parser.parseColon())
6301 return ::mlir::failure();
6302
6303 {
6304 ::zml::ComponentType type;
6305 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
6306 return ::mlir::failure();
6307 valRawTypes[0] = type;
6308 }
6309 {
6310 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
6311 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
6312 return ::mlir::failure();
6313 if (failed(verifyInherentAttrs(result.name, result.attributes, [&]() {
6314 return parser.emitError(loc) << "'" << result.name.getStringRef() << "' op ";
6315 })))
6316 return ::mlir::failure();
6317 }
6318 result.addTypes(valTypes);
6319 return ::mlir::success();
6320}
6321
6322void LitStrOp::print(::mlir::OpAsmPrinter &_odsPrinter) {
6323 _odsPrinter << ' ';
6324 _odsPrinter.printAttributeWithoutType(getValueAttr());
6325 _odsPrinter << ' ' << ":";
6326 _odsPrinter << ' ';
6327 {
6328 auto type = getVal().getType();
6329 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::zml::ComponentType>(type))
6330 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
6331 else
6332 _odsPrinter << type;
6333 }
6334 ::llvm::SmallVector<::llvm::StringRef, 2> elidedAttrs;
6335 elidedAttrs.push_back("value");
6336 _odsPrinter.printOptionalAttrDict((*this)->getAttrs(), elidedAttrs);
6337}

6340}

6682 std::next(getOperation()->result_begin(), valueRange.first + valueRange.second)};

6689::mlir::LogicalResult LitValOp::setPropertiesFromAttr(Properties &prop, ::mlir::Attribute attr, ::llvm::function_ref<::mlir::InFlightDiagnostic()> emitError) {
6690 ::mlir::DictionaryAttr dict = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::mlir::DictionaryAttr>(attr);
6691 if (!dict) {
6692 emitError() << "expected DictionaryAttr to set properties";
6693 return ::mlir::failure();
6694 }
6695
6696 {
6697 auto &propStorage = prop.value;
6698 auto attr = dict.get("value");
6699 if (attr || /*isRequired=*/true) {
6700 if (!attr) {
6701 emitError() << "expected key entry for value in DictionaryAttr to set "
6702 "Properties.";
6703 return ::mlir::failure();

6705 auto convertedAttr = ::llvm::dyn_cast<std::remove_reference_t<decltype(propStorage)>>(attr);
6706 if (convertedAttr) {
6707 propStorage = convertedAttr;
6708 } else {
6709 emitError() << "Invalid attribute `value` in property conversion: " << attr;
6710 return ::mlir::failure();
6711 }
6712 }
6713 }
6714 return ::mlir::success();
6715}

6823::mlir::LogicalResult LitValOp::verifyInvariantsImpl() {
6824 auto tblgen_value = getProperties().value; (void)tblgen_value;
6825 if (!tblgen_value) return emitOpError("requires attribute 'value'");
6826
6827 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops9(*this, tblgen_value, "value")))
6828 return ::mlir::failure();
6829 {
6830 unsigned index = 0; (void)index;
6831 auto valueGroup0 = getODSResults(0);
6832
6833 for (auto v : valueGroup0) {
6834 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_type_constraint_Ops0(*this, v.getType(), "result", index++)))
6835 return ::mlir::failure();
6836 }
6837 }
6838 return ::mlir::success();
6839}
6840
6841::mlir::LogicalResult LitValOp::verifyInvariants() {
6842 return verifyInvariantsImpl();
6843}
6844
6845::mlir::ParseResult LitValOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
6846 ::mlir::IntegerAttr valueAttr;
6847 ::mlir::Type valRawTypes[1];
6848 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> valTypes(valRawTypes);
6849
6850 if (parser.parseCustomAttributeWithFallback(valueAttr, parser.getBuilder().getIntegerType(64))) {
6851 return ::mlir::failure();
6852 }
6853 if (valueAttr) result.getOrAddProperties<LitValOp::Properties>().value = valueAttr;
6854 if (parser.parseColon())
6855 return ::mlir::failure();
6856
6857 {
6858 ::zml::ComponentType type;
6859 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
6860 return ::mlir::failure();
6861 valRawTypes[0] = type;
6862 }
6863 {
6864 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
6865 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
6866 return ::mlir::failure();
6867 if (failed(verifyInherentAttrs(result.name, result.attributes, [&]() {
6868 return parser.emitError(loc) << "'" << result.name.getStringRef() << "' op ";
6869 })))
6870 return ::mlir::failure();
6871 }
6872 result.addTypes(valTypes);
6873 return ::mlir::success();
6874}
6875
6876void LitValOp::print(::mlir::OpAsmPrinter &_odsPrinter) {
6877 _odsPrinter << ' ';
6878 _odsPrinter.printAttributeWithoutType(getValueAttr());
6879 _odsPrinter << ' ' << ":";
6880 _odsPrinter << ' ';
6881 {
6882 auto type = getVal().getType();
6883 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::zml::ComponentType>(type))
6884 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
6885 else
6886 _odsPrinter << type;
6887 }
6888 ::llvm::SmallVector<::llvm::StringRef, 2> elidedAttrs;
6889 elidedAttrs.push_back("value");
6890 _odsPrinter.printOptionalAttrDict((*this)->getAttrs(), elidedAttrs);
6891}

6894}

7259

7262 return ::mlir::failure();

7264 }

7267 auto valueGroup0 = getODSResults(0);

7281::mlir::ParseResult MakeExtOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
7282 ::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand inRawOperands[1];
7283 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand> inOperands(inRawOperands); ::llvm::SMLoc inOperandsLoc;
7284 (void)inOperandsLoc;
7285 ::mlir::Type inRawTypes[1];
7286 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> inTypes(inRawTypes);
7287 ::mlir::Type outRawTypes[1];
7288 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> outTypes(outRawTypes);
7289
7290 inOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
7291 if (parser.parseOperand(inRawOperands[0]))
7292 return ::mlir::failure();
7293 if (parser.parseColon())
7294 return ::mlir::failure();
7295
7296 {
7297 ::zml::ComponentType type;
7298 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
7299 return ::mlir::failure();
7300 inRawTypes[0] = type;
7301 }
7302 if (parser.parseArrow())
7303 return ::mlir::failure();
7304
7305 {
7306 ::zml::ComponentType type;
7307 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
7308 return ::mlir::failure();
7309 outRawTypes[0] = type;
7310 }
7311 {
7312 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
7313 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
7314 return ::mlir::failure();
7315 }
7316 result.addTypes(outTypes);
7317 if (parser.resolveOperands(inOperands, inTypes, inOperandsLoc, result.operands))
7318 return ::mlir::failure();
7319 return ::mlir::success();
7320}
7321
7322void MakeExtOp::print(::mlir::OpAsmPrinter &_odsPrinter) {
7323 _odsPrinter << ' ';
7324 _odsPrinter << getIn();
7325 _odsPrinter << ' ' << ":";
7326 _odsPrinter << ' ';
7327 {
7328 auto type = getIn().getType();
7329 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::zml::ComponentType>(type))
7330 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
7331 else
7332 _odsPrinter << type;
7333 }
7334 _odsPrinter << ' ' << "->";
7335 _odsPrinter << ' ';
7336 {
7337 auto type = getOut().getType();
7338 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::zml::ComponentType>(type))
7339 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
7340 else
7341 _odsPrinter << type;
7342 }
7343 ::llvm::SmallVector<::llvm::StringRef, 2> elidedAttrs;
7344 _odsPrinter.printOptionalAttrDict((*this)->getAttrs(), elidedAttrs);
7345}

7891::mlir::LogicalResult NegOp::verifyInvariantsImpl() {
7892 {
7893 unsigned index = 0; (void)index;
7894 auto valueGroup0 = getODSOperands(0);
7895
7896 for (auto v : valueGroup0) {
7897 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_type_constraint_Ops0(*this, v.getType(), "operand", index++)))
7898 return ::mlir::failure();
7899 }
7900 }
7901 {
7902 unsigned index = 0; (void)index;
7903 auto valueGroup0 = getODSResults(0);
7904
7905 for (auto v : valueGroup0) {

7907 return ::mlir::failure();

7917::mlir::ParseResult NegOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
7918 ::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand inRawOperands[1];
7919 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand> inOperands(inRawOperands); ::llvm::SMLoc inOperandsLoc;
7920 (void)inOperandsLoc;
7921 ::mlir::Type inRawTypes[1];
7922 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> inTypes(inRawTypes);
7923 ::mlir::Type outRawTypes[1];
7924 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> outTypes(outRawTypes);
7925
7926 inOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
7927 if (parser.parseOperand(inRawOperands[0]))
7928 return ::mlir::failure();
7929 if (parser.parseColon())
7930 return ::mlir::failure();
7931
7932 {
7933 ::zml::ComponentType type;
7934 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
7935 return ::mlir::failure();
7936 inRawTypes[0] = type;
7937 }
7938 if (parser.parseArrow())
7939 return ::mlir::failure();
7940
7941 {
7942 ::zml::ComponentType type;
7943 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
7944 return ::mlir::failure();
7945 outRawTypes[0] = type;
7946 }
7947 {
7948 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
7949 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
7950 return ::mlir::failure();
7951 }
7952 result.addTypes(outTypes);
7953 if (parser.resolveOperands(inOperands, inTypes, inOperandsLoc, result.operands))
7954 return ::mlir::failure();
7955 return ::mlir::success();
7956}

7958void NegOp::print(::mlir::OpAsmPrinter &_odsPrinter) {
7959 _odsPrinter << ' ';
7960 _odsPrinter << getIn();
7961 _odsPrinter << ' ' << ":";
7962 _odsPrinter << ' ';
7963 {
7964 auto type = getIn().getType();
7965 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::zml::ComponentType>(type))
7966 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
7967 else
7968 _odsPrinter << type;
7969 }
7970 _odsPrinter << ' ' << "->";
7971 _odsPrinter << ' ';
7972 {
7973 auto type = getOut().getType();
7974 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::zml::ComponentType>(type))
7975 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
7976 else
7977 _odsPrinter << type;
7978 }
7979 ::llvm::SmallVector<::llvm::StringRef, 2> elidedAttrs;
7980 _odsPrinter.printOptionalAttrDict((*this)->getAttrs(), elidedAttrs);
7981}

7996NewArrayOpGenericAdaptorBase::NewArrayOpGenericAdaptorBase(::mlir::DictionaryAttr attrs, const ::mlir::EmptyProperties &properties, ::mlir::RegionRange regions) : odsAttrs(attrs), odsRegions(regions) { if (odsAttrs)
7997 odsOpName.emplace("zml.new_array", odsAttrs.getContext());
7998}
7999
8000NewArrayOpGenericAdaptorBase::NewArrayOpGenericAdaptorBase(NewArrayOp op) : NewArrayOpGenericAdaptorBase(op->getAttrDictionary(), op.getProperties(), op->getRegions()) {}
8001
8002std::pair<unsigned, unsigned> NewArrayOpGenericAdaptorBase::getODSOperandIndexAndLength(unsigned index, unsigned odsOperandsSize) {
8003 bool isVariadic[] = {true};
8004 int prevVariadicCount = 0;
8005 for (unsigned i = 0; i < index; ++i)
8006 if (isVariadic[i]) ++prevVariadicCount;
8007
8008 // Calculate how many dynamic values a static variadic operand corresponds to.
8009 // This assumes all static variadic operands have the same dynamic value count.
8010 int variadicSize = (odsOperandsSize - 0) / 1;
8011 // `index` passed in as the parameter is the static index which counts each
8012 // operand (variadic or not) as size 1. So here for each previous static variadic
8013 // operand, we need to offset by (variadicSize - 1) to get where the dynamic
8014 // value pack for this static operand starts.
8015 int start = index + (variadicSize - 1) * prevVariadicCount;
8016 int size = isVariadic[index] ? variadicSize : 1;
8017 return {start, size};
8018}

8021 return odsAttrs;
8022}

8024} // namespace detail

8117::mlir::ParseResult NewArrayOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
8118 ::llvm::SmallVector<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand, 4> elementsOperands;
8119 ::llvm::SMLoc elementsOperandsLoc;
8120 (void)elementsOperandsLoc;
8121 ::llvm::SmallVector<::mlir::Type, 1> elementsTypes;
8122 ::mlir::Type resultRawTypes[1];
8123 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> resultTypes(resultRawTypes);
8124
8125 elementsOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
8126 if (parser.parseOperandList(elementsOperands))
8127 return ::mlir::failure();
8128 {
8129 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
8130 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
8131 return ::mlir::failure();
8132 }
8133 if (parser.parseColon())
8134 return ::mlir::failure();
8135 if (parser.parseLSquare())
8136 return ::mlir::failure();
8137
8138 if (parser.parseTypeList(elementsTypes))
8139 return ::mlir::failure();
8140 if (parser.parseRSquare())
8141 return ::mlir::failure();
8142 if (parser.parseComma())
8143 return ::mlir::failure();
8144
8145 {
8146 ::mlir::Type type;
8147 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
8148 return ::mlir::failure();
8149 resultRawTypes[0] = type;
8150 }
8151 result.addTypes(resultTypes);
8152 if (parser.resolveOperands(elementsOperands, elementsTypes, elementsOperandsLoc, result.operands))
8153 return ::mlir::failure();
8154 return ::mlir::success();
8155}

8323::mlir::ParseResult NopOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
8324 ::llvm::SmallVector<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand, 4> insOperands;
8325 ::llvm::SMLoc insOperandsLoc;
8326 (void)insOperandsLoc;
8327 ::llvm::SmallVector<::mlir::Type, 1> insTypes;
8328 ::llvm::SmallVector<::mlir::Type, 1> outsTypes;
8329
8330 insOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
8331 if (parser.parseOperandList(insOperands))
8332 return ::mlir::failure();
8333 if (!insOperands.empty()) {
8334 if (parser.parseColon())
8335 return ::mlir::failure();
8336
8337 if (parser.parseTypeList(insTypes))
8338 return ::mlir::failure();
8339 if (parser.parseArrow())
8340 return ::mlir::failure();
8341 }
8342
8343 if (parser.parseTypeList(outsTypes))
8344 return ::mlir::failure();
8345 {
8346 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
8347 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
8348 return ::mlir::failure();
8349 }
8350 result.addTypes(outsTypes);
8351 if (parser.resolveOperands(insOperands, insTypes, insOperandsLoc, result.operands))
8352 return ::mlir::failure();
8353 return ::mlir::success();
8354}

8356void NopOp::print(::mlir::OpAsmPrinter &_odsPrinter) {
8357 if (!getIns().empty()) {
8358 _odsPrinter << ' ';
8359 _odsPrinter << getIns();
8360 _odsPrinter << ' ' << ":";
8361 _odsPrinter << ' ';
8362 _odsPrinter << getIns().getTypes();
8363 _odsPrinter << ' ' << "->";
8364 }
8365 _odsPrinter << ' ';
8366 _odsPrinter << getOuts().getTypes();
8367 ::llvm::SmallVector<::llvm::StringRef, 2> elidedAttrs;
8368 _odsPrinter.printOptionalAttrDict((*this)->getAttrs(), elidedAttrs);
8369}

8384ReadArrayOpGenericAdaptorBase::ReadArrayOpGenericAdaptorBase(::mlir::DictionaryAttr attrs, const ::mlir::EmptyProperties &properties, ::mlir::RegionRange regions) : odsAttrs(attrs), odsRegions(regions) { if (odsAttrs)

8389
8390std::pair<unsigned, unsigned> ReadArrayOpGenericAdaptorBase::getODSOperandIndexAndLength(unsigned index, unsigned odsOperandsSize) {
8391 bool isVariadic[] = {false, true};
8392 int prevVariadicCount = 0;
8393 for (unsigned i = 0; i < index; ++i)
8394 if (isVariadic[i]) ++prevVariadicCount;
8395
8396 // Calculate how many dynamic values a static variadic operand corresponds to.
8397 // This assumes all static variadic operands have the same dynamic value count.
8398 int variadicSize = (odsOperandsSize - 1) / 1;
8399 // `index` passed in as the parameter is the static index which counts each
8400 // operand (variadic or not) as size 1. So here for each previous static variadic
8401 // operand, we need to offset by (variadicSize - 1) to get where the dynamic
8402 // value pack for this static operand starts.
8403 int start = index + (variadicSize - 1) * prevVariadicCount;
8404 int size = isVariadic[index] ? variadicSize : 1;
8405 return {start, size};
8406}

8409 return odsAttrs;
8410}

8426 // This assumes all static variadic operands have the same dynamic value count.
8427 int variadicSize = (getOperation()->getNumOperands() - 1) / 1;
8428 // `index` passed in as the parameter is the static index which counts each
8429 // operand (variadic or not) as size 1. So here for each previous static variadic
8430 // operand, we need to offset by (variadicSize - 1) to get where the dynamic
8431 // value pack for this static operand starts.
8432 int start = index + (variadicSize - 1) * prevVariadicCount;
8433 int size = isVariadic[index] ? variadicSize : 1;
8434 return {start, size};

8497::mlir::LogicalResult ReadArrayOp::verifyInvariantsImpl() {
8498 {
8499 unsigned index = 0; (void)index;
8500 auto valueGroup0 = getODSOperands(0);
8501
8502 for (auto v : valueGroup0) {
8503 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_type_constraint_Ops2(*this, v.getType(), "operand", index++)))
8504 return ::mlir::failure();
8505 }
8506 auto valueGroup1 = getODSOperands(1);
8507
8508 for (auto v : valueGroup1) {
8509 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_type_constraint_Ops3(*this, v.getType(), "operand", index++)))
8510 return ::mlir::failure();
8511 }
8512 }
8513 {
8514 unsigned index = 0; (void)index;
8515 auto valueGroup0 = getODSResults(0);
8516
8517 for (auto v : valueGroup0) {
8518 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_type_constraint_Ops2(*this, v.getType(), "result", index++)))
8519 return ::mlir::failure();
8520 }
8521 }
8522 return ::mlir::success();
8523}
