8529::mlir::ParseResult ReadArrayOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
8530 ::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand lvalueRawOperands[1];
8531 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand> lvalueOperands(lvalueRawOperands); ::llvm::SMLoc lvalueOperandsLoc;
8532 (void)lvalueOperandsLoc;
8533 ::llvm::SmallVector<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand, 4> indicesOperands;
8534 ::llvm::SMLoc indicesOperandsLoc;
8535 (void)indicesOperandsLoc;
8536 ::mlir::Type lvalueRawTypes[1];
8537 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> lvalueTypes(lvalueRawTypes);
8538 ::llvm::SmallVector<::mlir::Type, 1> indicesTypes;
8539 ::mlir::Type resultRawTypes[1];
8540 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> resultTypes(resultRawTypes);
8541
8542 lvalueOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
8543 if (parser.parseOperand(lvalueRawOperands[0]))
8544 return ::mlir::failure();
8545 if (parser.parseLSquare())
8546 return ::mlir::failure();
8547
8548 indicesOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
8549 if (parser.parseOperandList(indicesOperands))
8550 return ::mlir::failure();
8551 if (parser.parseRSquare())
8552 return ::mlir::failure();
8553 {
8554 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
8555 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
8556 return ::mlir::failure();
8557 }
8558 if (parser.parseColon())
8559 return ::mlir::failure();
8560
8561 {
8562 ::mlir::Type type;
8563 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
8564 return ::mlir::failure();
8565 lvalueRawTypes[0] = type;
8566 }
8567 if (parser.parseLSquare())
8568 return ::mlir::failure();
8569
8570 if (parser.parseTypeList(indicesTypes))
8571 return ::mlir::failure();
8572 if (parser.parseRSquare())
8573 return ::mlir::failure();
8574 if (parser.parseComma())
8575 return ::mlir::failure();
8576
8577 {
8578 ::mlir::Type type;
8579 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
8580 return ::mlir::failure();
8581 resultRawTypes[0] = type;
8582 }
8583 result.addTypes(resultTypes);
8584 if (parser.resolveOperands(lvalueOperands, lvalueTypes, lvalueOperandsLoc, result.operands))
8585 return ::mlir::failure();
8586 if (parser.resolveOperands(indicesOperands, indicesTypes, indicesOperandsLoc, result.operands))
8587 return ::mlir::failure();
8588 return ::mlir::success();
8589}
8590
8591void ReadArrayOp::print(::mlir::OpAsmPrinter &_odsPrinter) {
8592 _odsPrinter << ' ';
8593 _odsPrinter << getLvalue();
8594 _odsPrinter << "[";
8595 _odsPrinter << getIndices();
8596 _odsPrinter << "]";
8597 ::llvm::SmallVector<::llvm::StringRef, 2> elidedAttrs;
8598 _odsPrinter.printOptionalAttrDict((*this)->getAttrs(), elidedAttrs);
8599 _odsPrinter << ' ' << ":";
8600 _odsPrinter << ' ';
8601 {
8602 auto type = getLvalue().getType();
8603 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::mlir::Type>(type))
8604 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
8605 else
8606 _odsPrinter << type;
8607 }
8608 _odsPrinter << "[";
8609 _odsPrinter << getIndices().getTypes();
8610 _odsPrinter << "]";
8611 _odsPrinter << ",";
8612 _odsPrinter << ' ';
8613 {
8614 auto type = getResult().getType();
8615 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::mlir::Type>(type))
8616 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
8617 else
8618 _odsPrinter << type;
8619 }
8620}

8674

8679 return emitError(loc, "'zml.read_back' op ""attribute 'field' failed to satisfy constraint: string attribute");

8716::mlir::LogicalResult ReadBackOp::setPropertiesFromAttr(Properties &prop, ::mlir::Attribute attr, ::llvm::function_ref<::mlir::InFlightDiagnostic()> emitError) {
8717 ::mlir::DictionaryAttr dict = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::mlir::DictionaryAttr>(attr);
8718 if (!dict) {
8719 emitError() << "expected DictionaryAttr to set properties";
8720 return ::mlir::failure();
8721 }
8722
8723 {
8724 auto &propStorage = prop.distance;
8725 auto attr = dict.get("distance");
8726 if (attr || /*isRequired=*/true) {
8727 if (!attr) {
8728 emitError() << "expected key entry for distance in DictionaryAttr to set "
8729 "Properties.";
8730 return ::mlir::failure();
8731 }
8732 auto convertedAttr = ::llvm::dyn_cast<std::remove_reference_t<decltype(propStorage)>>(attr);
8733 if (convertedAttr) {
8734 propStorage = convertedAttr;
8735 } else {
8736 emitError() << "Invalid attribute `distance` in property conversion: " << attr;
8737 return ::mlir::failure();
8738 }
8739 }
8740 }
8741
8742 {
8743 auto &propStorage = prop.field;
8744 auto attr = dict.get("field");
8745 if (attr || /*isRequired=*/true) {
8746 if (!attr) {
8747 emitError() << "expected key entry for field in DictionaryAttr to set "
8748 "Properties.";
8749 return ::mlir::failure();
8750 }
8751 auto convertedAttr = ::llvm::dyn_cast<std::remove_reference_t<decltype(propStorage)>>(attr);
8752 if (convertedAttr) {
8753 propStorage = convertedAttr;
8754 } else {
8755 emitError() << "Invalid attribute `field` in property conversion: " << attr;
8756 return ::mlir::failure();
8757 }
8758 }
8759 }
8760 return ::mlir::success();
8761}

8763::mlir::Attribute ReadBackOp::getPropertiesAsAttr(::mlir::MLIRContext *ctx, const Properties &prop) {
8764 ::mlir::SmallVector<::mlir::NamedAttribute> attrs;
8765 ::mlir::Builder odsBuilder{ctx};
8766
8767 {
8768 const auto &propStorage = prop.distance;
8769 if (propStorage)
8770 attrs.push_back(odsBuilder.getNamedAttr("distance",
8771 propStorage));
8772 }
8773
8774 {
8775 const auto &propStorage = prop.field;
8776 if (propStorage)
8777 attrs.push_back(odsBuilder.getNamedAttr("field",
8778 propStorage));

8783 return {};

8918::mlir::LogicalResult ReadBackOp::verifyInvariantsImpl() {
8919 auto tblgen_distance = getProperties().distance; (void)tblgen_distance;
8920 if (!tblgen_distance) return emitOpError("requires attribute 'distance'");
8921 auto tblgen_field = getProperties().field; (void)tblgen_field;
8922 if (!tblgen_field) return emitOpError("requires attribute 'field'");
8923
8924 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops10(*this, tblgen_distance, "distance")))
8925 return ::mlir::failure();
8926
8927 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops0(*this, tblgen_field, "field")))
8928 return ::mlir::failure();
8929 {
8930 unsigned index = 0; (void)index;
8931 auto valueGroup0 = getODSOperands(0);
8932
8933 for (auto v : valueGroup0) {
8934 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_type_constraint_Ops0(*this, v.getType(), "operand", index++)))
8935 return ::mlir::failure();
8936 }
8937 }
8938 {
8939 unsigned index = 0; (void)index;
8940 auto valueGroup0 = getODSResults(0);
8941
8942 for (auto v : valueGroup0) {
8943 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_type_constraint_Ops2(*this, v.getType(), "result", index++)))
8944 return ::mlir::failure();
8945 }
8946 }
8947 return ::mlir::success();
8948}
8949
8950::mlir::LogicalResult ReadBackOp::verifyInvariants() {
8951 return verifyInvariantsImpl();
8952}
8953
8954::mlir::ParseResult ReadBackOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
8955 ::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand compRawOperands[1];
8956 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand> compOperands(compRawOperands); ::llvm::SMLoc compOperandsLoc;
8957 (void)compOperandsLoc;
8958 ::mlir::StringAttr fieldAttr;
8959 ::mlir::Type compRawTypes[1];
8960 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> compTypes(compRawTypes);
8961 ::mlir::Type resultRawTypes[1];
8962 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> resultTypes(resultRawTypes);
8963
8964 compOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
8965 if (parser.parseOperand(compRawOperands[0]))
8966 return ::mlir::failure();
8967 if (parser.parseLSquare())
8968 return ::mlir::failure();
8969
8970 if (parser.parseSymbolName(fieldAttr))
8971 return ::mlir::failure();
8972 if (fieldAttr) result.getOrAddProperties<ReadBackOp::Properties>().field = fieldAttr;
8973 if (parser.parseRSquare())
8974 return ::mlir::failure();
8975 if (parser.parseColon())
8976 return ::mlir::failure();
8977
8978 {
8979 ::zml::ComponentType type;
8980 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
8981 return ::mlir::failure();
8982 compRawTypes[0] = type;
8983 }
8984 if (parser.parseComma())
8985 return ::mlir::failure();
8986
8987 {
8988 ::mlir::Type type;
8989 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
8990 return ::mlir::failure();
8991 resultRawTypes[0] = type;
8992 }
8993 {
8994 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
8995 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
8996 return ::mlir::failure();
8997 if (failed(verifyInherentAttrs(result.name, result.attributes, [&]() {
8998 return parser.emitError(loc) << "'" << result.name.getStringRef() << "' op ";
8999 })))
9000 return ::mlir::failure();
9001 }
9002 result.addTypes(resultTypes);
9003 if (parser.resolveOperands(compOperands, compTypes, compOperandsLoc, result.operands))
9004 return ::mlir::failure();
9005 return ::mlir::success();
9006}
9007
9008void ReadBackOp::print(::mlir::OpAsmPrinter &_odsPrinter) {
9009 _odsPrinter << ' ';
9010 _odsPrinter << getComp();
9011 _odsPrinter << "[";
9012 _odsPrinter.printSymbolName(getFieldAttr().getValue());
9013 _odsPrinter << "]";
9014 _odsPrinter << ' ' << ":";
9015 _odsPrinter << ' ';
9016 {
9017 auto type = getComp().getType();
9018 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::zml::ComponentType>(type))
9019 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
9020 else
9021 _odsPrinter << type;
9022 }
9023 _odsPrinter << ",";
9024 _odsPrinter << ' ';
9025 {
9026 auto type = getResult().getType();
9027 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::mlir::Type>(type))
9028 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
9029 else
9030 _odsPrinter << type;
9031 }
9032 ::llvm::SmallVector<::llvm::StringRef, 2> elidedAttrs;
9033 elidedAttrs.push_back("field");
9034 _odsPrinter.printOptionalAttrDict((*this)->getAttrs(), elidedAttrs);
9035}

9116::mlir::LogicalResult ReadFieldOp::setPropertiesFromAttr(Properties &prop, ::mlir::Attribute attr, ::llvm::function_ref<::mlir::InFlightDiagnostic()> emitError) {
9117 ::mlir::DictionaryAttr dict = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::mlir::DictionaryAttr>(attr);
9118 if (!dict) {
9119 emitError() << "expected DictionaryAttr to set properties";
9120 return ::mlir::failure();
9121 }
9122

9125 auto attr = dict.get("field_name");

9129 "Properties.";
9130 return ::mlir::failure();

9133 if (convertedAttr) {
9134 propStorage = convertedAttr;
9135 } else {
9136 emitError() << "Invalid attribute `field_name` in property conversion: " << attr;
9137 return ::mlir::failure();
9138 }
9139 }
9140 }
9141 return ::mlir::success();

9285::mlir::ParseResult ReadFieldOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
9286 ::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand componentRawOperands[1];
9287 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand> componentOperands(componentRawOperands); ::llvm::SMLoc componentOperandsLoc;
9288 (void)componentOperandsLoc;
9289 ::mlir::FlatSymbolRefAttr field_nameAttr;
9290 ::mlir::Type componentRawTypes[1];
9291 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> componentTypes(componentRawTypes);
9292 ::mlir::Type valRawTypes[1];
9293 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> valTypes(valRawTypes);
9294
9295 componentOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
9296 if (parser.parseOperand(componentRawOperands[0]))
9297 return ::mlir::failure();
9298 if (parser.parseLSquare())
9299 return ::mlir::failure();
9300
9301 if (parser.parseCustomAttributeWithFallback(field_nameAttr, parser.getBuilder().getType<::mlir::NoneType>())) {
9302 return ::mlir::failure();
9303 }
9304 if (field_nameAttr) result.getOrAddProperties<ReadFieldOp::Properties>().field_name = field_nameAttr;
9305 if (parser.parseRSquare())
9306 return ::mlir::failure();
9307 {
9308 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
9309 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
9310 return ::mlir::failure();
9311 if (failed(verifyInherentAttrs(result.name, result.attributes, [&]() {
9312 return parser.emitError(loc) << "'" << result.name.getStringRef() << "' op ";
9313 })))
9314 return ::mlir::failure();
9315 }
9316 if (parser.parseColon())
9317 return ::mlir::failure();
9318
9319 {
9320 ::mlir::Type type;
9321 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
9322 return ::mlir::failure();
9323 componentRawTypes[0] = type;
9324 }
9325 if (parser.parseComma())
9326 return ::mlir::failure();
9327
9328 {
9329 ::mlir::Type type;
9330 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
9331 return ::mlir::failure();
9332 valRawTypes[0] = type;
9333 }
9334 result.addTypes(valTypes);
9335 if (parser.resolveOperands(componentOperands, componentTypes, componentOperandsLoc, result.operands))
9336 return ::mlir::failure();
9337 return ::mlir::success();
9338}

9456::mlir::ParseResult SelfOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
9457 std::unique_ptr<::mlir::Region> bodyRegion = std::make_unique<::mlir::Region>();
9458 ::llvm::SmallVector<::mlir::Type, 1> allResultTypes;
9459
9460 if (parser.parseRegion(*bodyRegion))
9461 return ::mlir::failure();
9462 {
9463 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
9464 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
9465 return ::mlir::failure();
9466 }
9467 if (parser.parseColon())
9468 return ::mlir::failure();
9469
9470 if (parser.parseTypeList(allResultTypes))
9471 return ::mlir::failure();
9472 result.addRegion(std::move(bodyRegion));
9473 result.addTypes(allResultTypes);
9474 return ::mlir::success();
9475}

9682::mlir::LogicalResult SetGlobalOp::verifyInvariantsImpl() {
9683 auto tblgen_name_ref = getProperties().name_ref; (void)tblgen_name_ref;
9684 if (!tblgen_name_ref) return emitOpError("requires attribute 'name_ref'");
9685
9686 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops6(*this, tblgen_name_ref, "name_ref")))
9687 return ::mlir::failure();
9688 {
9689 unsigned index = 0; (void)index;
9690 auto valueGroup0 = getODSOperands(0);
9691
9692 for (auto v : valueGroup0) {
9693 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_type_constraint_Ops2(*this, v.getType(), "operand", index++)))
9694 return ::mlir::failure();
9695 }
9696 }
9697 return ::mlir::success();
9698}
9699
9700::mlir::LogicalResult SetGlobalOp::verifyInvariants() {
9701 return verifyInvariantsImpl();
9702}
9703
9704::mlir::ParseResult SetGlobalOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
9705 ::mlir::SymbolRefAttr name_refAttr;
9706 ::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand valRawOperands[1];
9707 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand> valOperands(valRawOperands); ::llvm::SMLoc valOperandsLoc;
9708 (void)valOperandsLoc;
9709 ::mlir::Type valRawTypes[1];
9710 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> valTypes(valRawTypes);
9711
9712 if (parser.parseCustomAttributeWithFallback(name_refAttr, parser.getBuilder().getType<::mlir::NoneType>())) {
9713 return ::mlir::failure();
9714 }
9715 if (name_refAttr) result.getOrAddProperties<SetGlobalOp::Properties>().name_ref = name_refAttr;
9716 if (parser.parseEqual())
9717 return ::mlir::failure();
9718
9719 valOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
9720 if (parser.parseOperand(valRawOperands[0]))
9721 return ::mlir::failure();
9722 if (parser.parseColon())
9723 return ::mlir::failure();
9724
9725 {
9726 ::mlir::Type type;
9727 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
9728 return ::mlir::failure();
9729 valRawTypes[0] = type;
9730 }
9731 {
9732 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
9733 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
9734 return ::mlir::failure();
9735 if (failed(verifyInherentAttrs(result.name, result.attributes, [&]() {
9736 return parser.emitError(loc) << "'" << result.name.getStringRef() << "' op ";
9737 })))
9738 return ::mlir::failure();
9739 }
9740 if (parser.resolveOperands(valOperands, valTypes, valOperandsLoc, result.operands))
9741 return ::mlir::failure();
9742 return ::mlir::success();
9743}
9744
9745void SetGlobalOp::print(::mlir::OpAsmPrinter &_odsPrinter) {
9746 _odsPrinter << ' ';
9747 _odsPrinter.printAttributeWithoutType(getNameRefAttr());
9748 _odsPrinter << ' ' << "=";
9749 _odsPrinter << ' ';
9750 _odsPrinter << getVal();
9751 _odsPrinter << ' ' << ":";
9752 _odsPrinter << ' ';
9753 {
9754 auto type = getVal().getType();
9755 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::mlir::Type>(type))
9756 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
9757 else
9758 _odsPrinter << type;
9759 }
9760 ::llvm::SmallVector<::llvm::StringRef, 2> elidedAttrs;
9761 elidedAttrs.push_back("name_ref");
9762 _odsPrinter.printOptionalAttrDict((*this)->getAttrs(), elidedAttrs);
9763}

9879 auto tblgen_generic = getProperties().generic; (void)tblgen_generic;

10049 return ::mlir::success();
10050}
10051
10052::mlir::Attribute SplitComponentOp::getPropertiesAsAttr(::mlir::MLIRContext *ctx, const Properties &prop) {
10053 ::mlir::SmallVector<::mlir::NamedAttribute> attrs;
10054 ::mlir::Builder odsBuilder{ctx};
10055
10056 {
10057 const auto &propStorage = prop.builtin;
10058 if (propStorage)
10059 attrs.push_back(odsBuilder.getNamedAttr("builtin",
10060 propStorage));
10061 }
10062
10063 {
10064 const auto &propStorage = prop.function;
10065 if (propStorage)
10066 attrs.push_back(odsBuilder.getNamedAttr("function",
10067 propStorage));
10068 }
10069
10070 {
10071 const auto &propStorage = prop.generic;
10072 if (propStorage)
10073 attrs.push_back(odsBuilder.getNamedAttr("generic",
10074 propStorage));
10075 }
10076
10077 {
10078 const auto &propStorage = prop.params;
10079 if (propStorage)
10080 attrs.push_back(odsBuilder.getNamedAttr("params",
10081 propStorage));
10082 }
10083
10084 {
10085 const auto &propStorage = prop.sym_name;
10086 if (propStorage)
10087 attrs.push_back(odsBuilder.getNamedAttr("sym_name",
10088 propStorage));
10089 }
10090
10091 {
10092 const auto &propStorage = prop.usesBackVariables;
10093 if (propStorage)
10094 attrs.push_back(odsBuilder.getNamedAttr("usesBackVariables",
10095 propStorage));
10096 }
10097
10098 if (!attrs.empty())
10099 return odsBuilder.getDictionaryAttr(attrs);
10100 return {};
10101}

10103llvm::hash_code SplitComponentOp::computePropertiesHash(const Properties &prop) {
10104 return llvm::hash_combine(
10105 llvm::hash_value(prop.builtin.getAsOpaquePointer()),
10106 llvm::hash_value(prop.function.getAsOpaquePointer()),
10107 llvm::hash_value(prop.generic.getAsOpaquePointer()),
10108 llvm::hash_value(prop.params.getAsOpaquePointer()),
10109 llvm::hash_value(prop.sym_name.getAsOpaquePointer()),
10110 llvm::hash_value(prop.usesBackVariables.getAsOpaquePointer()));
10111}

10147 return;
10148 }
10149
10150 if (name == "params") {

10152 return;
10153 }
10154
10155 if (name == "sym_name") {
10156 prop.sym_name = ::llvm::dyn_cast_or_null<std::remove_reference_t<decltype(prop.sym_name)>>(value);
10157 return;
10158 }
10159
10160 if (name == "usesBackVariables") {
10161 prop.usesBackVariables = ::llvm::dyn_cast_or_null<std::remove_reference_t<decltype(prop.usesBackVariables)>>(value);
10162 return;
10163 }

10180::mlir::LogicalResult SplitComponentOp::verifyInherentAttrs(::mlir::OperationName opName, ::mlir::NamedAttrList &attrs, llvm::function_ref<::mlir::InFlightDiagnostic()> emitError) {
10181 {
10182 ::mlir::Attribute attr = attrs.get(getBuiltinAttrName(opName));
10183 if (attr && ::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops1(attr, "builtin", emitError)))
10184 return ::mlir::failure();
10185 }
10186
10187 {
10188 ::mlir::Attribute attr = attrs.get(getFunctionAttrName(opName));
10189 if (attr && ::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops1(attr, "function", emitError)))
10190 return ::mlir::failure();
10191 }
10192
10193 {
10194 ::mlir::Attribute attr = attrs.get(getGenericAttrName(opName));
10195 if (attr && ::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops1(attr, "generic", emitError)))
10196 return ::mlir::failure();
10197 }
10198
10199 {
10200 ::mlir::Attribute attr = attrs.get(getParamsAttrName(opName));
10201 if (attr && ::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops2(attr, "params", emitError)))
10202 return ::mlir::failure();
10203 }
10204
10205 {
10206 ::mlir::Attribute attr = attrs.get(getSymNameAttrName(opName));
10207 if (attr && ::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops0(attr, "sym_name", emitError)))
10208 return ::mlir::failure();
10209 }
10210
10211 {
10212 ::mlir::Attribute attr = attrs.get(getUsesBackVariablesAttrName(opName));
10213 if (attr && ::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops1(attr, "usesBackVariables", emitError)))
10214 return ::mlir::failure();
10215 }
10216 return ::mlir::success();
10217}

10222 return ::mlir::failure();
10223
10224 if (::mlir::failed(reader.readOptionalAttribute(prop.function)))

10228 return ::mlir::failure();

10234 return ::mlir::failure();

10237 return ::mlir::failure();

10493
10494::mlir::LogicalResult SplitComponentOp::verifyInvariantsImpl() {
10495 auto tblgen_builtin = getProperties().builtin; (void)tblgen_builtin;
10496 auto tblgen_function = getProperties().function; (void)tblgen_function;
10497 auto tblgen_generic = getProperties().generic; (void)tblgen_generic;
10498 auto tblgen_params = getProperties().params; (void)tblgen_params;
10499 auto tblgen_sym_name = getProperties().sym_name; (void)tblgen_sym_name;
10500 if (!tblgen_sym_name) return emitOpError("requires attribute 'sym_name'");
10501 auto tblgen_usesBackVariables = getProperties().usesBackVariables; (void)tblgen_usesBackVariables;
10502
10503 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops0(*this, tblgen_sym_name, "sym_name")))
10504 return ::mlir::failure();
10505
10506 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops1(*this, tblgen_function, "function")))
10507 return ::mlir::failure();
10508
10509 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops1(*this, tblgen_generic, "generic")))
10510 return ::mlir::failure();
10511
10512 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops1(*this, tblgen_builtin, "builtin")))
10513 return ::mlir::failure();
10514
10515 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops1(*this, tblgen_usesBackVariables, "usesBackVariables")))
10516 return ::mlir::failure();
10517
10518 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops2(*this, tblgen_params, "params")))
10519 return ::mlir::failure();
10520 {
10521 unsigned index = 0; (void)index;
10522
10523 for (auto &region : ::llvm::MutableArrayRef((*this)->getRegion(0)))
10524 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_region_constraint_Ops0(*this, region, "body", index++)))
10525 return ::mlir::failure();
10526 }
10527 return ::mlir::success();
10528}
10529
10530::mlir::LogicalResult SplitComponentOp::verifyInvariants() {
10531 return verifyInvariantsImpl();
10532}
10533
10534::mlir::ParseResult SplitComponentOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
10535 ::mlir::StringAttr sym_nameAttr;
10536 ::mlir::ArrayAttr paramsAttr;
10537 std::unique_ptr<::mlir::Region> bodyRegion = std::make_unique<::mlir::Region>();
10538
10539 if (parser.parseSymbolName(sym_nameAttr))
10540 return ::mlir::failure();
10541 if (sym_nameAttr) result.getOrAddProperties<SplitComponentOp::Properties>().sym_name = sym_nameAttr;
10542 if (::mlir::succeeded(parser.parseOptionalLess())) {
10543
10544 if (parser.parseCustomAttributeWithFallback(paramsAttr, parser.getBuilder().getType<::mlir::NoneType>())) {
10545 return ::mlir::failure();
10546 }
10547 if (paramsAttr) result.getOrAddProperties<SplitComponentOp::Properties>().params = paramsAttr;
10548 if (parser.parseGreater())
10549 return ::mlir::failure();
10550 }
10551 {
10552 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
10553 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDictWithKeyword(result.attributes))
10554 return ::mlir::failure();
10555 if (failed(verifyInherentAttrs(result.name, result.attributes, [&]() {
10556 return parser.emitError(loc) << "'" << result.name.getStringRef() << "' op ";
10557 })))
10558 return ::mlir::failure();
10559 }
10560
10561 if (parser.parseRegion(*bodyRegion))
10562 return ::mlir::failure();
10563
10564 if (bodyRegion->empty()) bodyRegion->emplaceBlock();
10565 result.addRegion(std::move(bodyRegion));
10566 return ::mlir::success();
10567}
10568
10569void SplitComponentOp::print(::mlir::OpAsmPrinter &_odsPrinter) {
10570 _odsPrinter << ' ';
10571 _odsPrinter.printSymbolName(getSymNameAttr().getValue());
10572 if (getParamsAttr()) {
10573 _odsPrinter << "<";
10574 _odsPrinter.printAttributeWithoutType(getParamsAttr());
10575 _odsPrinter << ">";
10576 }
10577 ::llvm::SmallVector<::llvm::StringRef, 2> elidedAttrs;
10578 elidedAttrs.push_back("sym_name");
10579 elidedAttrs.push_back("params");
10580 {
10581 ::mlir::Builder odsBuilder(getContext());
10582 ::mlir::Attribute attr = getFunctionAttr();
10583 if(attr && (attr == ((false) ? odsBuilder.getUnitAttr() : nullptr)))
10584 elidedAttrs.push_back("function");
10585 }
10586 {
10587 ::mlir::Builder odsBuilder(getContext());
10588 ::mlir::Attribute attr = getGenericAttr();
10589 if(attr && (attr == ((false) ? odsBuilder.getUnitAttr() : nullptr)))
10590 elidedAttrs.push_back("generic");
10591 }
10592 {
10593 ::mlir::Builder odsBuilder(getContext());
10594 ::mlir::Attribute attr = getBuiltinAttr();
10595 if(attr && (attr == ((false) ? odsBuilder.getUnitAttr() : nullptr)))
10596 elidedAttrs.push_back("builtin");
10597 }
10598 {
10599 ::mlir::Builder odsBuilder(getContext());
10600 ::mlir::Attribute attr = getUsesBackVariablesAttr();
10601 if(attr && (attr == ((false) ? odsBuilder.getUnitAttr() : nullptr)))
10602 elidedAttrs.push_back("usesBackVariables");
10603 }
10604 _odsPrinter.printOptionalAttrDictWithKeyword((*this)->getAttrs(), elidedAttrs);
10605 _odsPrinter << ' ';
10606 _odsPrinter.printRegion(getBody());
10607}

10735::mlir::ParseResult SubOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
10736 ::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand lhsRawOperands[1];
10737 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand> lhsOperands(lhsRawOperands); ::llvm::SMLoc lhsOperandsLoc;
10738 (void)lhsOperandsLoc;
10739 ::mlir::Type lhsRawTypes[1];
10740 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> lhsTypes(lhsRawTypes);
10741 ::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand rhsRawOperands[1];
10742 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand> rhsOperands(rhsRawOperands); ::llvm::SMLoc rhsOperandsLoc;
10743 (void)rhsOperandsLoc;
10744 ::mlir::Type rhsRawTypes[1];
10745 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> rhsTypes(rhsRawTypes);
10746 ::mlir::Type outRawTypes[1];
10747 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> outTypes(outRawTypes);
10748
10749 lhsOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
10750 if (parser.parseOperand(lhsRawOperands[0]))
10751 return ::mlir::failure();
10752 if (parser.parseColon())
10753 return ::mlir::failure();
10754
10755 {
10756 ::zml::ComponentType type;
10757 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
10758 return ::mlir::failure();
10759 lhsRawTypes[0] = type;
10760 }
10761 if (parser.parseComma())
10762 return ::mlir::failure();
10763
10764 rhsOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
10765 if (parser.parseOperand(rhsRawOperands[0]))
10766 return ::mlir::failure();
10767 if (parser.parseColon())
10768 return ::mlir::failure();
10769
10770 {
10771 ::zml::ComponentType type;
10772 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
10773 return ::mlir::failure();
10774 rhsRawTypes[0] = type;
10775 }
10776 if (parser.parseArrow())
10777 return ::mlir::failure();
10778
10779 {
10780 ::zml::ComponentType type;
10781 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
10782 return ::mlir::failure();
10783 outRawTypes[0] = type;
10784 }
10785 {
10786 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
10787 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
10788 return ::mlir::failure();
10789 }
10790 result.addTypes(outTypes);
10791 if (parser.resolveOperands(lhsOperands, lhsTypes, lhsOperandsLoc, result.operands))
10792 return ::mlir::failure();
10793 if (parser.resolveOperands(rhsOperands, rhsTypes, rhsOperandsLoc, result.operands))
10794 return ::mlir::failure();
10795 return ::mlir::success();
10796}
10797
10798void SubOp::print(::mlir::OpAsmPrinter &_odsPrinter) {
10799 _odsPrinter << ' ';
10800 _odsPrinter << getLhs();
10801 _odsPrinter << ' ' << ":";
10802 _odsPrinter << ' ';
10803 {
10804 auto type = getLhs().getType();
10805 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::zml::ComponentType>(type))
10806 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
10807 else
10808 _odsPrinter << type;
10809 }
10810 _odsPrinter << ",";
10811 _odsPrinter << ' ';
10812 _odsPrinter << getRhs();
10813 _odsPrinter << ' ' << ":";
10814 _odsPrinter << ' ';
10815 {
10816 auto type = getRhs().getType();
10817 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::zml::ComponentType>(type))
10818 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
10819 else
10820 _odsPrinter << type;
10821 }
10822 _odsPrinter << ' ' << "->";
10823 _odsPrinter << ' ';
10824 {
10825 auto type = getOut().getType();
10826 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::zml::ComponentType>(type))
10827 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
10828 else
10829 _odsPrinter << type;
10830 }
10831 ::llvm::SmallVector<::llvm::StringRef, 2> elidedAttrs;
10832 _odsPrinter.printOptionalAttrDict((*this)->getAttrs(), elidedAttrs);
10833}

11574VarArgsOpGenericAdaptorBase::VarArgsOpGenericAdaptorBase(::mlir::DictionaryAttr attrs, const ::mlir::EmptyProperties &properties, ::mlir::RegionRange regions) : odsAttrs(attrs), odsRegions(regions) { if (odsAttrs)
11575 odsOpName.emplace("zml.vargs", odsAttrs.getContext());

11578VarArgsOpGenericAdaptorBase::VarArgsOpGenericAdaptorBase(VarArgsOp op) : VarArgsOpGenericAdaptorBase(op->getAttrDictionary(), op.getProperties(), op->getRegions()) {}
11579
11580std::pair<unsigned, unsigned> VarArgsOpGenericAdaptorBase::getODSOperandIndexAndLength(unsigned index, unsigned odsOperandsSize) {
11581 bool isVariadic[] = {true};
11582 int prevVariadicCount = 0;
11583 for (unsigned i = 0; i < index; ++i)
11584 if (isVariadic[i]) ++prevVariadicCount;
11585
11586 // Calculate how many dynamic values a static variadic operand corresponds to.
11587 // This assumes all static variadic operands have the same dynamic value count.
11588 int variadicSize = (odsOperandsSize - 0) / 1;
11589 // `index` passed in as the parameter is the static index which counts each
11590 // operand (variadic or not) as size 1. So here for each previous static variadic
11591 // operand, we need to offset by (variadicSize - 1) to get where the dynamic
11592 // value pack for this static operand starts.
11593 int start = index + (variadicSize - 1) * prevVariadicCount;
11594 int size = isVariadic[index] ? variadicSize : 1;
11595 return {start, size};
11596}

11599 return odsAttrs;
11600}

11616 // This assumes all static variadic operands have the same dynamic value count.

11618 // `index` passed in as the parameter is the static index which counts each
11619 // operand (variadic or not) as size 1. So here for each previous static variadic
11620 // operand, we need to offset by (variadicSize - 1) to get where the dynamic

11673

11675 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_type_constraint_Ops6(*this, v.getType(), "operand", index++)))
11676 return ::mlir::failure();
11677 }
11678 }
11679 {
11680 unsigned index = 0; (void)index;
11681 auto valueGroup0 = getODSResults(0);
11682
11683 for (auto v : valueGroup0) {
11684 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_type_constraint_Ops9(*this, v.getType(), "result", index++)))
11685 return ::mlir::failure();
11686 }
11687 }
11688 if (!((
11689 ([](::mlir::Type inner, mlir::OperandRange::type_range elems) {
11690 for (auto e : elems) {
11691 if (!std::equal_to<>()(inner, e)) return false;
11692 }
11693 return true;
11694 })
11695(
11696 ::llvm::cast<::zml::VarArgsType>((*this->getODSResults(0).begin()).getType()).getInner()
11697, this->getODSOperands(0).getType()))))
11698 return emitOpError("failed to verify that inner type matches input operands");
11699 return ::mlir::success();

11706::mlir::ParseResult VarArgsOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
11707 ::llvm::SmallVector<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand, 4> elementsOperands;
11708 ::llvm::SMLoc elementsOperandsLoc;
11709 (void)elementsOperandsLoc;
11710 ::mlir::Type resultRawTypes[1];
11711 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> resultTypes(resultRawTypes);
11712
11713 elementsOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
11714 if (parser.parseOperandList(elementsOperands))
11715 return ::mlir::failure();
11716 {
11717 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
11718 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
11719 return ::mlir::failure();
11720 }
11721 if (parser.parseColon())
11722 return ::mlir::failure();
11723
11724 {
11725 ::zml::VarArgsType type;
11726 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
11727 return ::mlir::failure();
11728 resultRawTypes[0] = type;
11729 }
11730 for (::mlir::Type type : resultTypes) {
11731 (void)type;
11732 if (!((::llvm::isa<::zml::VarArgsType>(type)))) {
11733 return parser.emitError(parser.getNameLoc()) << "'result' must be variable number of arguments, but got " << type;
11734 }
11735 }
11736 result.addTypes(resultTypes);
11737 if (parser.resolveOperands(elementsOperands,
11738 ::llvm::cast<::zml::VarArgsType>(resultTypes[0]).getInner()
11739, elementsOperandsLoc, result.operands))
11740 return ::mlir::failure();
11741 return ::mlir::success();
11742}
11743
11744void VarArgsOp::print(::mlir::OpAsmPrinter &_odsPrinter) {
11745 _odsPrinter << ' ';
11746 _odsPrinter << getElements();
11747 ::llvm::SmallVector<::llvm::StringRef, 2> elidedAttrs;
11748 _odsPrinter.printOptionalAttrDict((*this)->getAttrs(), elidedAttrs);
11749 _odsPrinter << ' ' << ":";
11750 _odsPrinter << ' ';
11751 {
11752 auto type = getResult().getType();
11753 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::zml::VarArgsType>(type))
11754 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
11755 else
11756 _odsPrinter << type;
11757 }
11758}
11759

11770WriteArrayOpGenericAdaptorBase::WriteArrayOpGenericAdaptorBase(::mlir::DictionaryAttr attrs, const Properties &properties, ::mlir::RegionRange regions) : odsAttrs(attrs), properties(properties), odsRegions(regions) { if (odsAttrs)

11775
11776std::pair<unsigned, unsigned> WriteArrayOpGenericAdaptorBase::getODSOperandIndexAndLength(unsigned index, unsigned odsOperandsSize) {
11777 bool isVariadic[] = {false, true, false};
11778 int prevVariadicCount = 0;
11779 for (unsigned i = 0; i < index; ++i)
11780 if (isVariadic[i]) ++prevVariadicCount;
11781
11782 // Calculate how many dynamic values a static variadic operand corresponds to.
11783 // This assumes all static variadic operands have the same dynamic value count.
11784 int variadicSize = (odsOperandsSize - 2) / 1;
11785 // `index` passed in as the parameter is the static index which counts each
11786 // operand (variadic or not) as size 1. So here for each previous static variadic
11787 // operand, we need to offset by (variadicSize - 1) to get where the dynamic
11788 // value pack for this static operand starts.
11789 int start = index + (variadicSize - 1) * prevVariadicCount;
11790 int size = isVariadic[index] ? variadicSize : 1;
11791 return {start, size};
11792}

11796}

11800 if (!attr)
11801 attr = ((false) ? ::mlir::Builder(odsAttrs.getContext()).getUnitAttr() : nullptr);
11802 return attr;
11803}

11807 if (!attr)
11808 return ((false) ? ::mlir::Builder(odsAttrs.getContext()).getUnitAttr() : nullptr) != nullptr;
11809 return attr != nullptr;
11810}

11823std::pair<unsigned, unsigned> WriteArrayOp::getODSOperandIndexAndLength(unsigned index) {
11824 bool isVariadic[] = {false, true, false};
11825 int prevVariadicCount = 0;
11826 for (unsigned i = 0; i < index; ++i)
11827 if (isVariadic[i]) ++prevVariadicCount;
11828
11829 // Calculate how many dynamic values a static variadic operand corresponds to.
11830 // This assumes all static variadic operands have the same dynamic value count.
11831 int variadicSize = (getOperation()->getNumOperands() - 2) / 1;
11832 // `index` passed in as the parameter is the static index which counts each
11833 // operand (variadic or not) as size 1. So here for each previous static variadic
11834 // operand, we need to offset by (variadicSize - 1) to get where the dynamic
11835 // value pack for this static operand starts.
11836 int start = index + (variadicSize - 1) * prevVariadicCount;
11837 int size = isVariadic[index] ? variadicSize : 1;

11885::mlir::LogicalResult WriteArrayOp::setPropertiesFromAttr(Properties &prop, ::mlir::Attribute attr, ::llvm::function_ref<::mlir::InFlightDiagnostic()> emitError) {
11886 ::mlir::DictionaryAttr dict = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::mlir::DictionaryAttr>(attr);
11887 if (!dict) {
11888 emitError() << "expected DictionaryAttr to set properties";
11889 return ::mlir::failure();
11890 }
11891
11892 {
11893 auto &propStorage = prop.computeOnly;
11894 auto attr = dict.get("computeOnly");
11895 if (attr || /*isRequired=*/false) {
11896 if (!attr) {
11897 emitError() << "expected key entry for computeOnly in DictionaryAttr to set "
11898 "Properties.";
11899 return ::mlir::failure();
11900 }
11901 auto convertedAttr = ::llvm::dyn_cast<std::remove_reference_t<decltype(propStorage)>>(attr);
11902 if (convertedAttr) {
11903 propStorage = convertedAttr;
11904 } else {
11905 emitError() << "Invalid attribute `computeOnly` in property conversion: " << attr;
11906 return ::mlir::failure();
11907 }
11908 }
11909 }
11910 return ::mlir::success();
11911}

11914 ::mlir::SmallVector<::mlir::NamedAttribute> attrs;
11915 ::mlir::Builder odsBuilder{ctx};
11916
11917 {
11918 const auto &propStorage = prop.computeOnly;
11919 if (propStorage)
11920 attrs.push_back(odsBuilder.getNamedAttr("computeOnly",
11921 propStorage));

11923
11924 if (!attrs.empty())
11925 return odsBuilder.getDictionaryAttr(attrs);
11926 return {};

12048::mlir::LogicalResult WriteArrayOp::verifyInvariantsImpl() {
12049 auto tblgen_computeOnly = getProperties().computeOnly; (void)tblgen_computeOnly;
12050
12051 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops1(*this, tblgen_computeOnly, "computeOnly")))
12052 return ::mlir::failure();
12053 {
12054 unsigned index = 0; (void)index;
12055 auto valueGroup0 = getODSOperands(0);
12056
12057 for (auto v : valueGroup0) {
12058 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_type_constraint_Ops2(*this, v.getType(), "operand", index++)))
12059 return ::mlir::failure();
12060 }
12061 auto valueGroup1 = getODSOperands(1);
12062
12063 for (auto v : valueGroup1) {
12064 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_type_constraint_Ops3(*this, v.getType(), "operand", index++)))
12065 return ::mlir::failure();
12066 }
12067 auto valueGroup2 = getODSOperands(2);
12068
12069 for (auto v : valueGroup2) {
12070 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_type_constraint_Ops7(*this, v.getType(), "operand", index++)))
12071 return ::mlir::failure();
12072 }
12073 }
12074 return ::mlir::success();
12075}
12076
12077::mlir::LogicalResult WriteArrayOp::verifyInvariants() {
12078 return verifyInvariantsImpl();
12079}
12080
12081::mlir::ParseResult WriteArrayOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
12082 ::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand arrayRawOperands[1];
12083 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand> arrayOperands(arrayRawOperands); ::llvm::SMLoc arrayOperandsLoc;
12084 (void)arrayOperandsLoc;
12085 ::llvm::SmallVector<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand, 4> indicesOperands;
12086 ::llvm::SMLoc indicesOperandsLoc;
12087 (void)indicesOperandsLoc;
12088 ::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand valueRawOperands[1];
12089 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand> valueOperands(valueRawOperands); ::llvm::SMLoc valueOperandsLoc;
12090 (void)valueOperandsLoc;
12091 ::mlir::Type arrayRawTypes[1];
12092 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> arrayTypes(arrayRawTypes);
12093 ::llvm::SmallVector<::mlir::Type, 1> indicesTypes;
12094 ::mlir::Type valueRawTypes[1];
12095 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> valueTypes(valueRawTypes);
12096
12097 arrayOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
12098 if (parser.parseOperand(arrayRawOperands[0]))
12099 return ::mlir::failure();
12100 if (parser.parseLSquare())
12101 return ::mlir::failure();
12102
12103 indicesOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
12104 if (parser.parseOperandList(indicesOperands))
12105 return ::mlir::failure();
12106 if (parser.parseRSquare())
12107 return ::mlir::failure();
12108 if (parser.parseEqual())
12109 return ::mlir::failure();
12110
12111 valueOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
12112 if (parser.parseOperand(valueRawOperands[0]))
12113 return ::mlir::failure();
12114 {
12115 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
12116 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
12117 return ::mlir::failure();
12118 if (failed(verifyInherentAttrs(result.name, result.attributes, [&]() {
12119 return parser.emitError(loc) << "'" << result.name.getStringRef() << "' op ";
12120 })))
12121 return ::mlir::failure();
12122 }
12123 if (parser.parseColon())
12124 return ::mlir::failure();
12125
12126 {
12127 ::mlir::Type type;
12128 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
12129 return ::mlir::failure();
12130 arrayRawTypes[0] = type;
12131 }
12132 if (parser.parseLSquare())
12133 return ::mlir::failure();
12134
12135 if (parser.parseTypeList(indicesTypes))
12136 return ::mlir::failure();
12137 if (parser.parseRSquare())
12138 return ::mlir::failure();
12139 if (parser.parseComma())
12140 return ::mlir::failure();
12141
12142 {
12143 ::mlir::Type type;
12144 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
12145 return ::mlir::failure();
12146 valueRawTypes[0] = type;
12147 }
12148 if (parser.resolveOperands(arrayOperands, arrayTypes, arrayOperandsLoc, result.operands))
12149 return ::mlir::failure();
12150 if (parser.resolveOperands(indicesOperands, indicesTypes, indicesOperandsLoc, result.operands))
12151 return ::mlir::failure();
12152 if (parser.resolveOperands(valueOperands, valueTypes, valueOperandsLoc, result.operands))
12153 return ::mlir::failure();
12154 return ::mlir::success();
12155}
12156
12157void WriteArrayOp::print(::mlir::OpAsmPrinter &_odsPrinter) {
12158 _odsPrinter << ' ';
12159 _odsPrinter << getArray();
12160 _odsPrinter << "[";
12161 _odsPrinter << getIndices();
12162 _odsPrinter << "]";
12163 _odsPrinter << ' ' << "=";
12164 _odsPrinter << ' ';
12165 _odsPrinter << getValue();
12166 ::llvm::SmallVector<::llvm::StringRef, 2> elidedAttrs;
12167 {
12168 ::mlir::Builder odsBuilder(getContext());
12169 ::mlir::Attribute attr = getComputeOnlyAttr();
12170 if(attr && (attr == ((false) ? odsBuilder.getUnitAttr() : nullptr)))
12171 elidedAttrs.push_back("computeOnly");
12172 }
12173 _odsPrinter.printOptionalAttrDict((*this)->getAttrs(), elidedAttrs);
12174 _odsPrinter << ' ' << ":";
12175 _odsPrinter << ' ';
12176 {
12177 auto type = getArray().getType();
12178 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::mlir::Type>(type))
12179 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
12180 else
12181 _odsPrinter << type;
12182 }
12183 _odsPrinter << "[";
12184 _odsPrinter << getIndices().getTypes();
12185 _odsPrinter << "]";
12186 _odsPrinter << ",";
12187 _odsPrinter << ' ';
12188 {
12189 auto type = getValue().getType();
12190 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::mlir::Type>(type))
12191 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
12192 else
12193 _odsPrinter << type;
12194 }
12195}

12261::mlir::OpOperand &WriteFieldOp::getComponentMutable() {
12262 auto range = getODSOperandIndexAndLength(0);
12263 return getOperation()->getOpOperand(range.first);
12264}
12265
12266::mlir::OpOperand &WriteFieldOp::getValMutable() {
12267 auto range = getODSOperandIndexAndLength(1);
12268 return getOperation()->getOpOperand(range.first);
12269}

12271std::pair<unsigned, unsigned> WriteFieldOp::getODSResultIndexAndLength(unsigned index) {
12272 return {index, 1};
12273}
12274
12275::mlir::Operation::result_range WriteFieldOp::getODSResults(unsigned index) {
12276 auto valueRange = getODSResultIndexAndLength(index);
12277 return {std::next(getOperation()->result_begin(), valueRange.first),
12278 std::next(getOperation()->result_begin(), valueRange.first + valueRange.second)};
12279}
12280
12281::mlir::LogicalResult WriteFieldOp::setPropertiesFromAttr(Properties &prop, ::mlir::Attribute attr, ::llvm::function_ref<::mlir::InFlightDiagnostic()> emitError) {
12282 ::mlir::DictionaryAttr dict = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::mlir::DictionaryAttr>(attr);
12283 if (!dict) {
12284 emitError() << "expected DictionaryAttr to set properties";
12285 return ::mlir::failure();
12286 }
12287
12288 {
12289 auto &propStorage = prop.field_name;
12290 auto attr = dict.get("field_name");
12291 if (attr || /*isRequired=*/true) {
12292 if (!attr) {
12293 emitError() << "expected key entry for field_name in DictionaryAttr to set "
12294 "Properties.";
12295 return ::mlir::failure();
12296 }
12297 auto convertedAttr = ::llvm::dyn_cast<std::remove_reference_t<decltype(propStorage)>>(attr);
12298 if (convertedAttr) {
12299 propStorage = convertedAttr;
12300 } else {
12301 emitError() << "Invalid attribute `field_name` in property conversion: " << attr;
12302 return ::mlir::failure();
12303 }
12304 }
12305 }
12306 return ::mlir::success();
12307}
12308
12309::mlir::Attribute WriteFieldOp::getPropertiesAsAttr(::mlir::MLIRContext *ctx, const Properties &prop) {
12310 ::mlir::SmallVector<::mlir::NamedAttribute> attrs;
12311 ::mlir::Builder odsBuilder{ctx};
12312
12313 {
12314 const auto &propStorage = prop.field_name;
12315 if (propStorage)
12316 attrs.push_back(odsBuilder.getNamedAttr("field_name",
12317 propStorage));
12318 }
12319
12320 if (!attrs.empty())
12321 return odsBuilder.getDictionaryAttr(attrs);
12322 return {};
12323}
12324
12325llvm::hash_code WriteFieldOp::computePropertiesHash(const Properties &prop) {
12326 return llvm::hash_combine(
12327 llvm::hash_value(prop.field_name.getAsOpaquePointer()));
12328}

12330std::optional<mlir::Attribute> WriteFieldOp::getInherentAttr(::mlir::MLIRContext *ctx, const Properties &prop, llvm::StringRef name) {
12331 if (name == "field_name")
12332 return prop.field_name;
12333 return std::nullopt;
12334}

12336void WriteFieldOp::setInherentAttr(Properties &prop, llvm::StringRef name, mlir::Attribute value) {
12337 if (name == "field_name") {
12338 prop.field_name = ::llvm::dyn_cast_or_null<std::remove_reference_t<decltype(prop.field_name)>>(value);
12339 return;
12340 }
12341}
12342
12343void WriteFieldOp::populateInherentAttrs(::mlir::MLIRContext *ctx, const Properties &prop, ::mlir::NamedAttrList &attrs) {
12344 if (prop.field_name) attrs.append("field_name", prop.field_name);
12345}

12347::mlir::LogicalResult WriteFieldOp::verifyInherentAttrs(::mlir::OperationName opName, ::mlir::NamedAttrList &attrs, llvm::function_ref<::mlir::InFlightDiagnostic()> emitError) {
12348 {
12349 ::mlir::Attribute attr = attrs.get(getFieldNameAttrName(opName));
12350 if (attr && ::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops3(attr, "field_name", emitError)))
12351 return ::mlir::failure();
12352 }
12353 return ::mlir::success();
12354}

12413void WriteFieldOp::build(::mlir::OpBuilder &, ::mlir::OperationState &odsState, ::mlir::TypeRange resultTypes, ::mlir::ValueRange operands, ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::NamedAttribute> attributes) {
12414 assert(operands.size() == 2u && "mismatched number of parameters");
12415 odsState.addOperands(operands);
12416 odsState.addAttributes(attributes);
12417 assert(resultTypes.size() == 0u && "mismatched number of return types");
12418 odsState.addTypes(resultTypes);
12419}
12420
12421::mlir::LogicalResult WriteFieldOp::verifyInvariantsImpl() {
12422 auto tblgen_field_name = getProperties().field_name; (void)tblgen_field_name;
12423 if (!tblgen_field_name) return emitOpError("requires attribute 'field_name'");
12424
12425 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_attr_constraint_Ops3(*this, tblgen_field_name, "field_name")))
12426 return ::mlir::failure();
12427 {
12428 unsigned index = 0; (void)index;
12429 auto valueGroup0 = getODSOperands(0);
12430
12431 for (auto v : valueGroup0) {
12432 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_type_constraint_Ops2(*this, v.getType(), "operand", index++)))
12433 return ::mlir::failure();
12434 }
12435 auto valueGroup1 = getODSOperands(1);
12436
12437 for (auto v : valueGroup1) {
12438 if (::mlir::failed(__mlir_ods_local_type_constraint_Ops2(*this, v.getType(), "operand", index++)))
12439 return ::mlir::failure();
12440 }
12441 }
12442 return ::mlir::success();
12443}
12444
12445::mlir::LogicalResult WriteFieldOp::verifyInvariants() {
12446 return verifyInvariantsImpl();
12447}
12448
12449::mlir::ParseResult WriteFieldOp::parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result) {
12450 ::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand componentRawOperands[1];
12451 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand> componentOperands(componentRawOperands); ::llvm::SMLoc componentOperandsLoc;
12452 (void)componentOperandsLoc;
12453 ::mlir::FlatSymbolRefAttr field_nameAttr;
12454 ::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand valRawOperands[1];
12455 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::OpAsmParser::UnresolvedOperand> valOperands(valRawOperands); ::llvm::SMLoc valOperandsLoc;
12456 (void)valOperandsLoc;
12457 ::mlir::Type componentRawTypes[1];
12458 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> componentTypes(componentRawTypes);
12459 ::mlir::Type valRawTypes[1];
12460 ::llvm::ArrayRef<::mlir::Type> valTypes(valRawTypes);
12461
12462 componentOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
12463 if (parser.parseOperand(componentRawOperands[0]))
12464 return ::mlir::failure();
12465 if (parser.parseLSquare())
12466 return ::mlir::failure();
12467
12468 if (parser.parseCustomAttributeWithFallback(field_nameAttr, parser.getBuilder().getType<::mlir::NoneType>())) {
12469 return ::mlir::failure();
12470 }
12471 if (field_nameAttr) result.getOrAddProperties<WriteFieldOp::Properties>().field_name = field_nameAttr;
12472 if (parser.parseRSquare())
12473 return ::mlir::failure();
12474 if (parser.parseEqual())
12475 return ::mlir::failure();
12476
12477 valOperandsLoc = parser.getCurrentLocation();
12478 if (parser.parseOperand(valRawOperands[0]))
12479 return ::mlir::failure();
12480 {
12481 auto loc = parser.getCurrentLocation();(void)loc;
12482 if (parser.parseOptionalAttrDict(result.attributes))
12483 return ::mlir::failure();
12484 if (failed(verifyInherentAttrs(result.name, result.attributes, [&]() {
12485 return parser.emitError(loc) << "'" << result.name.getStringRef() << "' op ";
12486 })))
12487 return ::mlir::failure();
12488 }
12489 if (parser.parseColon())
12490 return ::mlir::failure();
12491
12492 {
12493 ::mlir::Type type;
12494 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
12495 return ::mlir::failure();
12496 componentRawTypes[0] = type;
12497 }
12498 if (parser.parseComma())
12499 return ::mlir::failure();
12500
12501 {
12502 ::mlir::Type type;
12503 if (parser.parseCustomTypeWithFallback(type))
12504 return ::mlir::failure();
12505 valRawTypes[0] = type;
12506 }
12507 if (parser.resolveOperands(componentOperands, componentTypes, componentOperandsLoc, result.operands))
12508 return ::mlir::failure();
12509 if (parser.resolveOperands(valOperands, valTypes, valOperandsLoc, result.operands))
12510 return ::mlir::failure();
12511 return ::mlir::success();
12512}
12513
12514void WriteFieldOp::print(::mlir::OpAsmPrinter &_odsPrinter) {
12515 _odsPrinter << ' ';
12516 _odsPrinter << getComponent();
12517 _odsPrinter << "[";
12518 _odsPrinter.printAttributeWithoutType(getFieldNameAttr());
12519 _odsPrinter << "]";
12520 _odsPrinter << ' ' << "=";
12521 _odsPrinter << ' ';
12522 _odsPrinter << getVal();
12523 ::llvm::SmallVector<::llvm::StringRef, 2> elidedAttrs;
12524 elidedAttrs.push_back("field_name");
12525 _odsPrinter.printOptionalAttrDict((*this)->getAttrs(), elidedAttrs);
12526 _odsPrinter << ' ' << ":";
12527 _odsPrinter << ' ';
12528 {
12529 auto type = getComponent().getType();
12530 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::mlir::Type>(type))
12531 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
12532 else
12533 _odsPrinter << type;
12534 }
12535 _odsPrinter << ",";
12536 _odsPrinter << ' ';
12537 {
12538 auto type = getVal().getType();
12539 if (auto validType = ::llvm::dyn_cast<::mlir::Type>(type))
12540 _odsPrinter.printStrippedAttrOrType(validType);
12541 else
12542 _odsPrinter << type;
12543 }
12544}
